Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\}美国华纳兄弟影片公司 {\fs14\}出品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\}美国DC漫画公司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋，给我看\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rachel, let me see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-借我看看 -谁找到就是谁的，这是我找到的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Can I see? -Finders keepers. And I found it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我家的花园\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In my garden.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,谁找到就是谁的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Finders keepers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,妈！ 阿尔弗雷德！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Mom! Mr. Alfred!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你又在做梦吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Did you have dream?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的恶梦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Nightmare.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,比这地方更可怕？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Worse than this place?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要跟你打架\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They are going to fight you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-又要打？ -不打死你绝不罢休\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Again? -Until they kill you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那就在吃早餐前打死我吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Can they kill me before breakfast?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,臭小子，你活在地狱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You are in hell, little man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,而我就是魔王\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And I am the devil.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是魔王\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're not the devil.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的沙包\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're practice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,关到禁闭室\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Solitary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么？ -为了保护\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Why? -For protection.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-我才不需要保护 -保护他们不被你打死\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I don't need protection. -Protection for them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,进去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Get in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么想打击罪犯…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Are you so desperate to fight criminals...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜入狱和他们单挑？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...that you lock yourself in to take them on one at a time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我一共有七个对手\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Actually, there were seven of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我只算到有六个，韦恩先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I counted six, Mr. Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我的名字？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}How do you know my name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯·韦恩仍是个大人物\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The world is too small for someone like Bruce Wayne to disappear...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你有多么落魄潦倒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...no matter how deep he chooses to sink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,敝姓杜卡 我是忍者大师的代言人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}My name is merely Ducard, but I speak for Ra's al Ghul...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他是犯罪集团的克星\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...a man greatly feared by the criminal underworld.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以指引你一条明路\N{\fe238}{\fs14}A man who can offer you a path.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你凭什么认为我需要指引？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What makes you think I need a path?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你这种人是自愿来这种地方\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Someone like you is only here by choice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你想深入了解罪犯的世界\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You have been exploring the criminal fraternity...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你的目的是什么\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but whatever your original intentions...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经迷失了方向\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...you have become truly lost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,忍者大师能指引我走哪条路？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And what path can Ra's al Ghul offer?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他一样痛恨邪恶力量\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The path of a man who shares his hatred of evil...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你也希望能伸张正义\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and wishes to serve true justice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是影武者联盟之路\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The path of the League of Shadows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-你们是以暴制暴的私刑者 -并不是\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You're vigilantes. -No, no, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在你争我夺之中失利的人 才会变成以暴制暴的私刑者\N{\fe238}{\fs14}A vigilante is just a man lost in the scramble for his own gratification.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会被击毁或遭囚禁\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He can be destroyed or locked up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…如果你能够超越自我极限\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But if you make yourself more than just a man...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为一个崇高理想全心投入\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...if you devote yourself to an ideal...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就无法阻止你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and if they can't stop you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你也将成为另一种人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...then you become something else entirely.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么人？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Which is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,传奇英雄，韦恩先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Legend, Mr. Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,明天你将被释放\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Tomorrow, you will be released.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想打击更凶狠的罪犯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}If you are bored of brawling with thieves and want to achieve something...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,东边的山坡有一种罕见的蓝花\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...there is a rare blue flower that grows on the eastern slopes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,摘下一朵蓝花\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Pick one of these flowers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能把它带到山巅\N{\fe238}{\fs14}If you can carry it to the top of the mountain...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也许就能找到你当初在寻找的东西\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...you may find what you were looking for in the first place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我在寻找什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And what was I looking for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你自己知道\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Only you can know that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,回去，你一定要回头\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You turn back. You go back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,忍者大师？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Ra's al Ghul?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,且慢\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你在寻找什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What are you seeking?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我在寻找…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I seek...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,打击犯罪、伸张正义的方法\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...the means to fight injustice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让制造恐惧的恶徒…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}To turn fear...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,心生恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...against those who prey on the fearful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你要让别人心生恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}To manipulate the fears in others...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就必须先战胜自己内心的恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...you must first master your own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备开战了吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Are you ready to begin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我连站都站不起来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I can... I can barely stand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,死神不会等你准备好\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Death does not wait for you to be ready!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,死神绝不手下留情！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Death is not considerate or fair!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你面对死神吧，不容有失\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And make no mistake, here you face death.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,虎爪\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Tiger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,柔术\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Jujitsu.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,豹掌\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Panther.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,身手不错，但这不是儿戏\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're skilled. But this is not a dance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你仍然害怕\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And you are afraid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是怕我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But not of me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我，韦恩先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Tell us, Mr. Wayne...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...what do you fear?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了，没事了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's okay. It's okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会有事的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You'll be okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老爷，我要叫救护车吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Will we be needing an ambulance, Master Wayne?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我先替他接骨，待会再照Ｘ光\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No, I'll set the bone and take him for an x-ray later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，老爷\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Very good, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-对不起，老爷 -别担心，他没事\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I'm very sorry, sir. I've told... -Don't worry. It's fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你跌得很惨，对吧，少爷？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Took quite a fall, didn't we, Master Bruce?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么跌倒，布鲁斯？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And why do we fall?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才能学会站起来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So we can learn to pick ourselves up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只是小跌了一下，轻微骨折而已\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Just a little fall. It's just a small fracture.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你又想到那些蝙蝠？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The bats again?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道它们为什么攻击你吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You know why they attacked you, don't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-因为它们怕你 -它们怕我？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-They were afraid of you. -Afraid of me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,每种生物都有恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}All creatures feel fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就连可怕的怪物也有？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Even the scary ones?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是可怕的怪物\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Especially the scary ones.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你看样东西\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I got something to show you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想你妈会喜欢吗？ -当然会\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You think your mother will like them? -Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-你该起床了吧？ -好啦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I think it's time to get up. -Maybe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不准赖床\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No going back to bed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，高架铁路是你建造的吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Did you build this train, Dad?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哥谭市对韦恩家族很好 但这城市日渐没落\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gotham's been good to our family, but the city's been suffering.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小老百姓的日子过得很辛苦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}People less fortunate than us have been enduring very hard times.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我们建造经济的大众交通工具 把全体市民连结在一起\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So we built a new, cheap, public transportation system to unite the city.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,正中央就是…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And at the center...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,韦恩大楼\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...Wayne Tower.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在那里上班吗？ -不，我在医院工作\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Is that where you work? -No, I work at the hospital.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我把公司交给了比我更好的人管理\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I leave the running of our company to much better men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-更好的人？ -嗯…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Better? -Well...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,比我对做生意更有兴趣的人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...more interested men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以走吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Can we go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我们走吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Okay. Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-布鲁斯，你怎么了？ -不是他，是我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What's wrong, Bruce? -No, no. It was me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是我想要出来透透气\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I just needed some fresh air.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,歌剧听久了很累人，对吧？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}A little bit of opera goes a long way. Right, Bruce?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回家吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come on. Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,皮夹和珠宝，快点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Wallets, jewelry. Come on, fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-没问题 -快点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-That's fine. -Fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Take it easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,别冲动\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Take it easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Here you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系，没关系\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's fine. It's fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把皮夹拿去，放过我们\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now just take it and go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要那串珍珠项链 -喂…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I said, jewelry. -Hey...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Thomas!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Don't be afraid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你父亲的大衣吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Is this your father's?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,穿好了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}There you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,戈登\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gordon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Good news.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们逮到凶手了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We got him, son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不用操心\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're in excellent hands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会好好打理公司\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We'll be watching the empire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,等你长大了再让你接管\N{\fe238}{\fs14}When you grow up, it'll be waiting for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我替你准备了晚餐\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I thought I might prepare a little supper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-好吧 -阿尔弗雷德？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Very well. -Alfred?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-是，布鲁斯少爷 -都是我的错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Yes, Master Bruce? -It was my fault, Alfred.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-我叫他们离开的 -不是\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I made them leave the theater. -No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-要是我不害怕… -这不是你的错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-If I hadn't gotten scared... -It was nothing that you did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是凶手一个人的错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It was him, and him alone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Do you understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想念他们，我好想念他们\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I miss them, Alfred. I miss them so much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是，布鲁斯少爷\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So do I, Master Bruce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So do I.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是认为是你害死你父母的吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And do you still feel responsible for your parents' death?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我的愤怒比罪恶感更多\N{\fe238}{\fs14}My anger outweighs my guilt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你学会了用愤怒代替罪恶感\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You have learned to bury your guilt with anger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我会教你接受它并面对事实\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I will teach you to confront it and to face the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以一个人对付六个人 我要教你一个人对付六百人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You know how to fight six men. We can teach you how to engage 600.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道怎么把自己藏起来 我可以教你怎么隐形\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You know how to disappear. We can teach you to become truly invisible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,隐形？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Invisible?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,忍者的隐形术全是靠耐心 和矫捷的身手\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The ninja understands that invisibility is a matter of patience and agility.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,耳听四面、眼观八方\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Always mind your surroundings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,忍者会运用火药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Ninjitsu employs explosive powders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-做为武器？ -或是障眼法\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-As weapons? -Or distractions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,戏剧效果和障眼法很有效\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Theatricality and deception are powerful agents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能让敌人把你当成凡人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You must become more than just a man in the mind of your opponent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是谁？ -一个农夫\N{\fe238}{\fs14}BRUCE: Who is he? -He was a farmer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他为了抢邻居的农地杀人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Then he tried to take his neighbor's land and became a murderer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在变成一名囚犯 -他会有什么下场？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Now he is a prisoner. -What'll happen to him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人就要偿命，不能姑息养奸\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Justice. Crime cannot be tolerated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,社会漠不关心才会让治安败坏\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Criminals thrive on the indulgence of society's understanding.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你父母的死不是你的错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your parents' death was not your fault.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是你父亲的错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It was your father's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能改变他不敢反击的事实\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Anger does not change the fact that your father failed to act.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-对方的手上有枪 -那能阻止你吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-The man had a gun. -Would that stop you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受过武术训练\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I've had training.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是重点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The training is nothing!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,决心才重要\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Will is everything!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,主动出击的决心\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The will to act.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yield.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你并没有打败我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You haven't beaten me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了杀敌失去重心\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You have sacrificed sure footing for a killing stroke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,用力磨擦胸口\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rub your chest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手可以帮你取暖\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your arms will take care of themselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你比你父亲更坚强\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You are stronger than your father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不了解我父亲\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You didn't know my father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解你内心的愤怒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But I know the rage that drives you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你的愤怒让你暂时忘却伤痛 直到你无法承受\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That impossible anger strangling the grief...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对亲人的思念\N{\fe238}{\fs14}until the memory of your loved one is just poison in your veins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天你会希望他们不存在\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And one day, you catch yourself wishing the person you loved had never existed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好让你的痛苦消失\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...so you'd be spared your pain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是一直都住在山上\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I wasn't always here in the mountains.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有过一个妻子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Once, I had a wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我一生的最爱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}My great love.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她惨遭杀害\N{\fe238}{\fs14}She was taken from me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你一样学会不能纵容坏人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Like you, I was forced to learn there are those without decency...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对他们绝对不能手下留情\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...who must be fought without hesitation, without pity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,愤怒给了你很大的力量\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your anger gives you great power.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但若不学会控制，它会毁了你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But if you let it, it will destroy you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,愤怒差点毁了我一生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...as it almost did me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是如何平息怒气？ -报仇\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What stopped it? -Vengeance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我没有用\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That's no help to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Why, Bruce?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不为父母报仇？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Why could you not avenge your parents?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,听证会后你要回普林斯顿大学\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Will you be heading back to Princeton after the hearing, sir...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你愿意多留一、两天？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...or can I persuade you to stay on for a day or two?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要回去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm not heading back at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不喜欢那里？ -我很喜欢\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You don't like it there? -I like it fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只是校方不喜欢我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They just don't feel the same way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-我安排你睡在主卧室 -不用\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I've prepared the master bedroom. -No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡我的房间就行\N{\fe238}{\fs14}My room will be fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言，韦恩宅邸是你的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}With all due respect, sir, Wayne Manor is your house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不，这是我父亲的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No, Alfred, it's my father's house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-你父亲过世了，少爷 -这地方是他的陵墓\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Your father is dead. -This place is a mausoleum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿把它的一砖一瓦拆掉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}If I have my way, I'll pull the damn thing down brick by brick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是韦恩家族世代相传的宅邸\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This house, Master Wayne, has sheltered six generations of your family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛在乎？ 这又不是你家\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Why do you give a damn, Alfred? It's not your family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我之所以在乎是因为一位好人…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I give a damn because a good man once made me responsible...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,把他心爱的独子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...for what was most precious to him...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,托付给我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...in the whole world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯小姐要载你到法院\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Miss Dawes has offered to drive you to the hearing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她大概想劝你不要去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}She probably hopes to talk you out of going.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该把过去也埋在地下吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Should I just bury the past out there with my parents, Alfred?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能告诉你该如何面对过去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I wouldn't presume to tell you what to do with your past, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有很多人关心你的未来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Just know that there are those of us who care about what you do with your future.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没放弃我，是吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Haven't given up on me yet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,永远都不会\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Never.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德一向都把炼奶放在最上面\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Alfred still keeps the condensed milk on the top shelf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他不知道你已长高、拿得到了吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hasn't he noticed you're tall enough to reach now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜那是老习惯吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Old habits die hard, I guess.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们小时候一样有办法拿到 -没错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Never used to stop us anyway. -No, it didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲好吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}How's your mom?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她很怀念这地方\N{\fe238}{\fs14}She misses this place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一样\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So do I.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只可惜现在已经人事全非了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But it's nothing without the people who made it what it was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-只有阿尔弗雷德还在这里 -还有你呀\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Now there's only Alfred. -And you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不会留下来，瑞秋 -你只是回来参加听证会\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I'm not staying, Rachel. -You're just back for the hearing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道谁也无法阻止你去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce, I don't suppose there's any way to convince you not to come.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这场听证会总得有人…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Someone at this proceeding...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,代表我父母出席\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...should stand for my parents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都很爱你的父母\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We all loved your parents, Bruce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-凶手齐利的行为不可原谅 -但是你的上司却要让他出狱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What Chill did is unforgivable. -Then why is your boss letting him go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他和卡麦·法康尼是牢友\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In prison, he shared a cell with Carmine Falcone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他愿意出庭作证交换提前假释\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He learned things, and he will testify in exchange for early parole.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.73,0:24:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋，他杀死我父母\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rachel, this man killed my parents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.41,0:24:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能忘记这件事\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I cannot let that pass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.31,0:24:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能了解我的心情\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And I need you to understand that, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,经济大萧条害齐利先生走投无路\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The depression hit working people, like Mr. Chill, hardest of all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.71,0:24:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他的罪行令人发指 但他是走投无路才铤而走险\N{\fe238}{\fs14}His crime was appalling, yes, but it was motivated not by greed but by desperation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.09,0:24:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他已服刑14年，并将协助我们\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Given the 14 years served, as well as his extraordinary level of cooperation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.19,0:24:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,侦办地检署最重大的案件\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...with one of this office's most important investigations...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.86,0:24:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我们要求让他假释出狱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...we strongly endorse his petition for early release.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,齐利先生？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Mr. Chill?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.00,0:24:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your Honor...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.54,0:24:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都为我做的事深感悔恨\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...not a day goes by that I don't wish I could take back what I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.27,0:24:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时的确是走投无路\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Sure, I was desperate, like a lot of people back then...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.71,0:25:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但这不能改变我的所作所为\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but that don't change what I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有一位韦恩家族成员在场\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I gather there is a member of the Wayne family here today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.52,0:25:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他有话要说吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Has he got anything to say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.50,0:25:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-他从侧门出来了 -他从侧门出来了，各位！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-He's coming out the side! -He's coming out the side, guys!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.54,0:25:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-他来了 -他来了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce Wayne!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.15,0:25:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,乔，乔！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Joe! Hey, Joe!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.55,0:25:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,法康尼老大向你问好\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Falcone says hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.36,0:25:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，布鲁斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come on, Bruce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.33,0:25:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不必看到这一幕\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We don't need to see this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.70,0:26:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要看\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.40,0:26:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,法官坚持要举行公开听证会\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The DA couldn't understand why Judge Faden insisted on making the hearing public.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.57,0:26:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定是被法康尼老大收买了 让齐利公开露面\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Falcone paid him off to get Chill out in the open.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.17,0:26:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我应该感谢他们才对\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Maybe I should thank them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.61,0:26:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不是说真的 -也许我是说真的，瑞秋\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You don't mean that. -What if I do, Rachel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.34,0:26:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是该为我父母伸张正义\N{\fe238}{\fs14}My parents deserved justice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.45,0:26:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是伸张正义而是报仇雪恨\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're not talking about justice. You're talking about revenge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.52,0:26:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-有时候这两者是一样的 -不，绝对不一样\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Sometimes, they're the same. -No, they're never the same.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.59,0:26:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,伸张正义是为了维持社会和谐 报仇只是为了逞一时之快\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Justice is about harmony. Revenge is about you making yourself feel better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.32,0:26:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-所以才会有公正的司法制度 -司法制度早已名存实亡\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-It's why we have an impartial system. -Your system is broken.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.70,0:26:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你想伸张正义就要忘却伤痛\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You care about justice? Look beyond your own pain, Bruce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.97,0:26:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个城市已经沉沦腐败\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This city is rotting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.60,0:26:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说经济大萧条已成历史，才怪\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They talk about the depression as if it's history. It's not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.54,0:26:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老百姓的日子越来越苦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Things are worse than ever here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.21,0:26:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,黑帮老大法康尼趁火打劫、无恶不作\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Falcone floods our streets with crime and drugs...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.94,0:26:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,逼人走上不归路，满街都是齐利之辈\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...preying on the desperate, creating new Joe Chills every day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.04,0:26:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他也许没有亲手杀死你父母\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Falcone may not have killed your parents, Bruce...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.21,0:27:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,却毁了他们代表的一切\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but he's destroying everything that they stood for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.25,0:27:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你想感谢他就去吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You wanna thank him for that? Here you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.02,0:27:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道他在哪里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We all know where to find him. As long as he keeps the bad people rich...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.56,0:27:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只要他继续为非作歹 就没有人动得了他\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and the good people scared, no one'll touch him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.36,0:27:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你父母这种仗义执言的好人 找不到了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Good people like your parents, who'll stand against injustice, they're gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.70,0:27:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没人挺身而出，哥谭市就完了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What chance does Gotham have when the good people do nothing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.54,0:27:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不是你说的好人 -什么意思？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I'm not one of your good people, Rachel. -What do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.21,0:27:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这些年来我一直想杀他 现在没机会了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}All these years, I wanted to kill him. Now I can't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.53,0:27:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲会以你为耻\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your father would be ashamed of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.66,0:28:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你本人看来比报上的照片高大\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're taller than you look in the tabloids, Mr. Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.63,0:28:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你没带枪？ 真瞧不起人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No gun? I'm insulted.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.67,0:28:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-你大可以寄张感谢卡给我就好 -我不是来感谢你的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You could've just sent a thank-you note. -I didn't come here to thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.71,0:28:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告诉你并不是人人都怕你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I came to show you that not everyone in Gotham's afraid of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.58,0:28:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,认识我的人才怕我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Only those who know me, kid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.55,0:28:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己看，这里有两位市议员\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Look around you. You'll see two councilmen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.35,0:28:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一位工会代表，两名警察\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...a union official, couple off-duty cops...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.62,0:29:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,和一位法官\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and a judge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.42,0:29:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我大可以在他们面前毙了你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I wouldn't have a second's hesitation of blowing your head off in front of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.86,0:29:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这种权力是买不到的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now, that's power you can't buy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.22,0:29:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是恐惧的力量\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That's the power of fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.09,0:29:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不怕你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm not afraid of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.49,0:29:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你自以为能完全豁出去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Because you think you got nothing to lose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.56,0:29:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你没有想清楚\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But you haven't thought it through.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.37,0:29:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你没想到在地检署工作 青梅竹马的女朋友\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You haven't thought about your lady friend in the DA's office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.67,0:29:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有对你忠心耿耿的老管家\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You haven't thought about your old butler. Bang!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.24,0:29:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这种人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}People from your world...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.74,0:29:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有太多牵挂了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...have so much to lose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.28,0:29:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为你爹娘被人一枪打死\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now, you think because your mommy and your daddy got shot...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.78,0:29:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就能了解人性的丑陋吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...you know about the ugly side of life, but you don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.92,0:29:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本就不知道民间疾苦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You've never tasted desperate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.19,0:29:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哥谭市的天之骄子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're... You're Bruce Wayne, the prince of Gotham.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.92,0:29:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你的大名无人不知、无人不晓\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You'd have to go 1000 miles to meet someone who didn't know your name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.49,0:29:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,别正气凛然地跑来当一个大英雄\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So don't come here with your anger, trying to prove something to yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.96,0:29:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全不了解犯罪世界\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is a world you'll never understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.23,0:29:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不了解的事\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And you always fear...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.43,0:29:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,永远会让你害怕\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...what you don't understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.77,0:30:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.74,0:30:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是很佩服你的胆识\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yeah, you got spirit, kid. I'll give you that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.78,0:30:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你比你老子更带种\N{\fe238}{\fs14}More than your old man anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.91,0:30:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,齐利在牢里跟我提到你父母\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In the joint, Chill told me about the night he killed your parents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.39,0:30:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你老爸向他…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He said your father begged for mercy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.99,0:30:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跪地求饶\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Begged.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.89,0:30:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,像条狗一样哀号\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Like a dog.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.14,0:30:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定是小费给太少了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Should've tipped better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.91,0:30:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要什么？ -你的外套\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-For what? -Your jacket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.31,0:30:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.02,0:31:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吧，这件大衣不错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hey, hey, hey. Let me have it. It's a nice coat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.65,0:31:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别被人看到你穿这件大衣\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Be careful who sees you with that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.36,0:31:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们会来找我 -谁？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-They're gonna come looking for me. -Who?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.73,0:31:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Everyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.73,0:31:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这件…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.66,0:31:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这件大衣真不错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's a nice coat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.95,0:31:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,当你和坏人同流合污，会同情他们吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}When you lived among the criminals, did you start to pity them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.48,0:31:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,会的，当我第一次为了吃饭偷东西时\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The first time I stole so that I wouldn't starve, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.39,0:31:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我突然失去了是非善恶的观念\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I lost many assumptions about the simple nature of right and wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.13,0:31:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,当我到处闯荡\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And when I traveled...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.40,0:31:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我嚐到犯罪前的恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}... I learned the fear before a crime...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.87,0:31:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,以及得手后的兴奋\N{\fe238}{\fs14}... and the thrill of success.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.30,0:31:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我从来没变成坏人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But I never became one of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.67,0:32:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想说他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.64,0:32:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我管你叫什么，你只是个犯人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Fool. What do I care what your name is? You're a criminal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.81,0:32:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是犯人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm not a criminal{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.98,0:32:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你去和这批货的主人说吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Tell that to the guy who owned these.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.98,0:32:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,(韦恩企业，中国制造)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.01,0:32:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了克服内心恐惧 并洞悉犯罪心理而走遍全世界\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You've traveled the world to understand the criminal mind and conquer your fears.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.09,0:32:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是罪犯的内心并不复杂\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But a criminal is not complicated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.36,0:32:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你真正害怕的是自己的内心\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And what you really fear is inside yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.86,0:32:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕你自己的力量\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You fear your own power.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.59,0:32:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你也害怕你内心的愤怒…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You fear your anger...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.33,0:32:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,会逼你做出伟大或可怕的事\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...the drive to do great or terrible things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.77,0:32:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须克服你的内心恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now you must journey inwards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.97,0:32:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You are ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.04,0:32:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,吸气\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Breathe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.02,0:32:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,用力吸气\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Breathe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.89,0:33:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的恐惧吸进去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Breathe in your fears.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.39,0:33:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,面对你的恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Face them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.90,0:33:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你要成为恐惧本身，才能克服它\N{\fe238}{\fs14}To conquer fear, you must become fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.87,0:33:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须造成别人的恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You must bask in the fear of other men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.70,0:33:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而大家都害怕看不见的东西\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And men fear most what they cannot see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.35,0:33:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须让人想到你就害怕\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You have to become a terrible thought.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.79,0:33:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,成为死神化身\N{\fe238}{\fs14}A wraith.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.70,0:33:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,让坏人闻风丧胆\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You have to become an idea!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.94,0:34:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,感受恐惧如何模糊你的感官\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Feel terror cloud your senses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.75,0:34:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让恐惧的力量扭曲你的身心\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Feel its power to distort.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.92,0:34:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,掌控你的一切\N{\fe238}{\fs14}To control.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.22,0:34:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这股恐惧的力量才会属于你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And know that this power can be yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.57,0:34:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拥抱你最深层的恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Embrace your worst fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.24,0:34:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和恐惧的黑暗力量融为一体\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Become one with the darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.36,0:35:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,全神贯注\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Focus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.36,0:35:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,全心投入\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Concentrate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.70,0:35:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,随心所欲控制你的全身\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Master your senses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.89,0:35:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能露出你的行踪\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You cannot leave any sign.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.69,0:35:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I haven't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.20,0:35:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Impressive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.68,0:36:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经消除你的恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We have purged your fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.55,0:36:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以当这批勇士的首领\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You are ready to lead these men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.35,0:36:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以加入影武者联盟\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You are ready to become a member of the League of Shadows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.52,0:36:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先要证明你矢志维护正义\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But first, you must demonstrate your commitment to justice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.44,0:36:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.27,0:36:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是刽子手\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm no executioner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.11,0:36:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人不会对你手下留情\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your compassion is a weakness your enemies will not share.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.15,0:36:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是重点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That's why it's so important.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.68,0:36:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们和他们的不同\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It separates us from them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.58,0:36:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你想打击犯罪，他就是杀人犯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You want to fight criminals. This man is a murderer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.15,0:36:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-他应该接受审判 -受谁审判？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-This man should be tried. DUCARD: By whom?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.12,0:36:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,让贪污腐败的法官来审判？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Corrupt bureaucrats?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.99,0:36:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,坏人根本没把法律放在眼里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Criminals mock society's laws.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.66,0:36:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你比任何人都清楚这一点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You know this better than most.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.83,0:37:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能率领他们\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You cannot lead these men...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.60,0:37:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你能不择手段打击犯罪\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...unless you are prepared to do what is necessary to defeat evil.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.20,0:37:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要率领他们到哪里？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And where would I be leading these men?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.17,0:37:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哥谭市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gotham.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.60,0:37:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哥谭市的天之骄子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}As Gotham's favored son...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.84,0:37:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你有能力瓦解哥谭市的恶势力\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...you will be ideally placed to strike at the heart of criminality.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.54,0:37:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-我该怎么做？ -哥谭市的气数已尽\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-How? -Gotham's time has come.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.48,0:37:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟君士坦丁堡和古罗马一样\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Like Constantinople or Rome before it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.98,0:37:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哥谭市已经沦为万恶的城市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...the city has become a breeding ground for suffering and injustice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.35,0:37:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它无可救药，必须将它毁灭\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It is beyond saving and must be allowed to die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.12,0:37:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这是影武者联盟最重要的任务\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is the most important function of the League of Shadows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.59,0:37:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我们数百年来的使命\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It is one we've performed for centuries.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.03,0:37:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哥谭市…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gotham...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.93,0:37:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要被摧毁\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...must be destroyed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.14,0:37:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会信这种鬼话吧？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You can't believe in this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.87,0:37:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,忍者大师将我们从 内心最黑暗的角落拯救出来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Ra's al Ghul rescued us from the darkest corners of our own hearts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.58,0:38:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他要求我们以勇气 行当行之事回报他\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What he asks in return is the courage to do what is necessary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.21,0:38:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回哥谭市对付这类坏人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I will go back to Gotham and I will fight men like this...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.72,0:38:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不会当刽子手\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but I will not become an executioner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.45,0:38:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯，别这样\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.19,0:38:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你要想清楚，你已不能回头\N{\fe238}{\fs14}For your own sake, there is no turning back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.35,0:38:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是在干什么？ -行我当行之事\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What are you doing? -What's necessary, my friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.30,0:41:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟他说你救他一命\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I will tell him you saved his life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.19,0:41:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,韦恩少爷，你消失好一阵子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Master Wayne, you've been gone a long time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.89,0:41:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊 -你这身打扮很时髦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Yes, I have. -You look very fashionable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.69,0:41:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只是有点脏\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Apart from the mud.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.43,0:41:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你这次会待很久吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Are you coming back to Gotham for long, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.26,0:41:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,需要待多久就待多久\N{\fe238}{\fs14}As long as it takes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.66,0:41:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让哥谭市市民知道\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I want to show the people...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.33,0:41:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这城市不属于贪官与罪犯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...their city doesn't belong to the criminals and the corrupt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.94,0:41:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,经济大萧条期间你爸为了消弭贫穷\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In the depression, your father nearly bankrupted Wayne Enterprises...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.30,0:41:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎倾家荡产\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...combating poverty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.74,0:41:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他相信他能让有钱人共襄盛举 拯救哥谭市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He believed his example could inspire the wealthy of Gotham to save their city.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.54,0:41:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他成功了吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Did it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.28,0:41:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In a way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.91,0:42:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他惨遭谋杀，为有钱有势的人敲响警钟\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Their murder shocked the wealthy and the powerful into action.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.98,0:42:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,人们的漠不关心 唯有戏剧性大逆转才能唤醒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}People need dramatic examples to shake them out of apathy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.22,0:42:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,身为布鲁斯·韦恩做不了什么\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I can't do that as Bruce Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.06,0:42:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是个血肉之躯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}As a man...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.76,0:42:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很容易被忽视、摧毁\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...I'm flesh and blood, I can be ignored, destroyed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.33,0:42:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是成为正义化身\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But as a symbol...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.73,0:42:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我就永远不会被击败\N{\fe238}{\fs14}As a symbol, I can be incorruptible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.53,0:42:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-永远正气长存 -什么化身？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I can be everlasting. -What symbol?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.77,0:42:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一种原始的…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Something elemental...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.60,0:42:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的化身\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...something terrifying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.40,0:42:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你单枪匹马对抗犯罪集团\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I assume that as you take on the underworld...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.67,0:42:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为这化身是会 保护你关心的人不被报复\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...this symbol is a persona to protect those you care about from reprisals?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.98,0:42:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的是瑞秋吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're thinking about Rachel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.51,0:42:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我说的是我自己\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Actually, sir, I was thinking of myself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.92,0:42:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有人知道我回来吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Have you told anyone I'm coming back?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.85,0:42:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢让人知道你死而复生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I couldn't figure the legal ramifications of bringing you back from the dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.22,0:42:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-死而复生？ -你失踪了七年\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Dead? -You've been gone seven years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.29,0:42:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你对外宣布我死了？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You had me declared dead?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.72,0:42:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是厄尔先生，他要让公司上市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Actually, it was Mr. Earle. He's taking the company public.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.79,0:42:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他也要把你的股票卖掉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He wanted to liquidate your majority shareholding.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.23,0:42:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那些股票值很多钱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Those shares are worth quite a bit of money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.73,0:43:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好我把全部财产都留给你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, it's a good thing I left everything to you, then.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.00,0:43:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，少爷\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Quite so, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.90,0:43:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的劳斯莱斯可以借你开 回来时别忘了加满油\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And you can borrow the Rolls, if you like. Just bring it back with a full tank.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.74,0:43:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为萨兹先生会试图自杀并危害他人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In my opinion, Mr. Zsaz is as much a danger to himself as to others...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.84,0:43:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因此监狱并不适合他\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and prison is probably not the best environment for his rehabilitation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.72,0:43:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-克莱恩医师 -道斯小姐\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Dr. Crane. -Miss Dawes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.49,0:43:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的认为黑道杀手不该坐牢？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You think a man who butchers people for the mob doesn't belong in jail?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.92,0:43:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我若不这么认为，就不会替他辩护\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I would hardly have testified to that otherwise, would I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.76,0:43:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,法康尼老大有三个杀手\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is the third of Falcone's thugs you've had declared insane...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.03,0:43:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,被你送进精神疗养院\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and moved into your asylum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.66,0:43:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,混黑道一定很容易被逼疯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The work offered by organized crime must have an attraction to the insane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.83,0:43:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,或是被收买\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Or the corrupt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.07,0:43:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,芬奇先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Mr. Finch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.01,0:43:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好劝劝道斯小姐\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You should check with Miss Dawes here...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.97,0:44:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要无凭无据对我提出指控\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...just what implications your office has authorized her to make. If any.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.31,0:44:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-瑞秋，你这是在做什么？ -你又是在做什么，卡尔？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What are you doing? -What are you doing, Carl?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.82,0:44:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在保护你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}FINCH: Looking out for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.69,0:44:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,法康尼收买了一半的政府官员\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Falcone has half the city bought and paid for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.76,0:44:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-放弃吧 -你怎么能这么说？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Drop it. -How can you say that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.99,0:44:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我痛恨法康尼，但我更关心你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Because as much as I care about getting Falcone, I care more about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.86,0:44:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你对我好\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That's sweet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.57,0:44:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不能接受\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We've been through all that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.02,0:44:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,又有一只蝙蝠飞进来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}ALFRED: Blessed bat again, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.93,0:45:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的巢穴一定在地底\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They nest somewhere in the grounds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.20,0:47:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不帮你了，有人对我起疑心\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No more favors. Someone is sniffing around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.07,0:47:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你，你帮我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hey, I scratch your back, you scratch mine, doc.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.20,0:47:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我替你们把货运进来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm bringing in the shipments.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.27,0:47:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有付你钱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We are paying you for that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.67,0:47:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,付钱并不算是帮我的忙\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Maybe money isn't as interesting to me as favors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.67,0:47:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你并不怕我，法康尼先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I am more than aware that you are not intimidated by me, Mr. Falcone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.65,0:47:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是等我的老板来了以后…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But you know who I'm working for, and when he gets here...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.88,0:47:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他要来哥谭市？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He... He's coming to Gotham?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.98,0:47:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yes, he is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.58,0:47:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了以后会想听到…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And when he gets here, he's not going to wanna hear...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.22,0:47:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了几个小混混危害我们的行动\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...that you've endangered our operation just to get your thugs out of jail time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.29,0:47:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁在找你麻烦？ -地检署的一个女孩\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Who's bothering you? -There's a girl at the DA's office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.13,0:47:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们用钱收买她 -她不要钱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-We'll buy her off. -Not this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.06,0:47:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是理想主义者\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Idealist, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.13,0:47:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有办法对付这种人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, there's an answer to that too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.23,0:47:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-我并不想知道 -你非知道不可\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I don't want to know. -Yes, you do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.21,0:47:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,(韦恩大楼)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.37,0:47:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,其它部门的业绩有稳健的成长\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No, we are showing very healthy growth in these sectors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.98,0:47:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯·韦恩绝对不会同意…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I don't think Thomas Wayne would have viewed heavy-arms manufacture...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.35,0:48:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让公司变成军火制造商\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...as a suitable cornerstone for our business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.88,0:48:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那是二十年前的事，佛德瑞\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, that's 20 years ago, Fredericks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.99,0:48:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯·韦恩都死了二十年\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I think after 20 years we can allow ourselves...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.32,0:48:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不必再管他怎么想\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...to stop thinking about what Thomas Wayne would have done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.36,0:48:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,早安，厄尔先生办公室\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Good morning, Mr. Earle's office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.39,0:48:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，他确定明天会出席晚宴\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yes, he's confirmed for the dinner tomorrow evening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.86,0:48:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,早安，我来见厄尔先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Good morning. I'm here to see Mr. Earle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.33,0:48:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,请问贵姓大名？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.30,0:48:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯·韦恩\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.84,0:48:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯也许不会让公司上市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Thomas would probably not have taken the company public.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.51,0:48:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们为了公司一定要这么做\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But that is what we, as responsible managers, are going to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.31,0:48:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,洁西卡？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Jessica?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.95,0:48:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,洁西卡？ 你在哪里？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Jessica? Where are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.65,0:48:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-盯着小白球看… -你为什么不接电话？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Eye on the ball, and... -Why is no one answering the phone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.59,0:48:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,放心，对方一定会再打来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's Wayne Enterprises, Mr. Earle. I'm sure they'll call back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.09,0:48:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯？ 你不是死了吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce? You're supposed to be dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.76,0:48:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你失望了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm sorry to disappoint.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.86,0:48:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要看看这份文件 -你见到他了吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I need you to take a look at this. -Have you seen him yet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.90,0:48:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁？ -韦恩\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Who? -Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.76,0:49:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,新闻整天都在播，他回来了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's been all over the news. He's back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.77,0:49:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,请你了解这件事势在必行\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm sure you realize I can't stop the big machine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.84,0:49:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,时势如此\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Too many wheels turning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.27,0:49:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-公司一定要上市 -我了解\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-We're going public. -I understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.74,0:49:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会分到不少钱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And I'll be handsomely rewarded for my shares.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.71,0:49:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不想干涉公司行政\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm not looking to interfere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.75,0:49:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-我只想要一份工作 -哦？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I am looking for a job. -Oh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.02,0:49:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想多了解我的家族企业\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I just want to get to know the company that my family built.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.39,0:49:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你想先进哪个部门？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Any ideas where you would start?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.65,0:49:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我对应用科技部门有兴趣\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Applied Sciences caught my eye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.39,0:49:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,福克斯的部门\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Fox's department.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.29,0:49:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我会通知他\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'll let him know you're coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.20,0:49:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟你爸长得很像\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You look like him. Your dad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.73,0:49:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是韦恩家族唯一的遗孤\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're the only one left of the Wayne family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.60,0:49:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的家，欢迎回家\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is where you belong. Welcome home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.84,0:49:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,环保科技、军火、消费产品\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Environmental procedures, defense projects, consumer products.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.87,0:49:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是实验原型 并没有进入量产阶段\N{\fe238}{\fs14}All prototypes. None in production.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.78,0:49:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-完全没有 -完全没有？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-On any level whatsoever. -None?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.41,0:49:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么跟你说这部门的？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What did they tell you this place was?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.45,0:49:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么都没说\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They didn't tell me anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.92,0:50:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,厄尔倒是跟我说得很明白\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Earle told me exactly what it was when he sent me down here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.86,0:50:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我被打入冷宫\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Dead end.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.49,0:50:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好让我不在董事会上找麻烦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Place to keep me from causing the board any more trouble.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.76,0:50:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.43,0:50:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-你曾经是公司董事？ -当你父亲还在的时候\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You were on the board? -When your father ran things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.06,0:50:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-你认识我父亲？ -是啊\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You knew my father? -Oh, yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.13,0:50:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我协助他建造高架铁路系统\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Helped him build his train.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.37,0:50:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,到了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Here we are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.67,0:50:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,多功能强化防护带\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Kevlar utility harness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.67,0:50:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,汽动式磁力钩爪枪\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gas-powered, magnetic grapple gun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.81,0:50:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,承受重量高达１５８公斤\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The 350-pound test monofilament.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.45,0:50:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸设计的铁路系统很棒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Wonderful project, your dad's train.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.15,0:50:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,每一条路线都直达韦恩大楼 水电管线也直接连到这里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Routed it right into Wayne Tower, along with the water and power utilities.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.92,0:50:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让韦恩大楼成为哥谭市的命脉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Kind of made Wayne Tower the unofficial center of Gotham City.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.36,0:50:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,厄尔却让它荒废，请看\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Of course, Earle let it go to rot. Here we are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.86,0:50:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,先锋部队的装甲衣\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Nomex survival suit for advanced infantry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.20,0:50:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,克维拉纤维，强化护肘护膝\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Kevlar biweave, reinforced joints.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.26,0:50:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-防裂材质？ -连刀都刺不穿\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Tear-resistant? -This sucker will stop a knife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.80,0:51:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-防弹吗？ -刀枪不入\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Bulletproof? -Anything but a straight shot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.20,0:51:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不量产？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Why didn't they put it into production? -Bean counters didn't think...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.94,0:51:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,军方认为士兵的命不值３０万元\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...a soldier's life was worth 300 grand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.71,0:51:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么对这些感兴趣？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So, what's your interest in it, Mr. Wayne?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.81,0:51:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想借来用\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I want to borrow it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.51,0:51:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做洞穴探险\N{\fe238}{\fs14}For spelunking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.15,0:51:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,洞穴探险？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Spelunking?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.62,0:51:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对，到山洞探险\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yeah, you know, cave diving?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.62,0:51:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有人会在山洞向你开枪吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You expecting to run into much gunfire in these caves?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.62,0:51:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望让厄尔知道…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Look, I'd rather Mr. Earle didn't know about me borrowing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.06,0:51:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,韦恩先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Mr. Wayne...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.53,0:51:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...the way I see it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.90,0:51:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切都是你的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...all this stuff is yours anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.30,0:51:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，试试看\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Okay. Give it a try.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.94,0:51:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个好地方\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Charming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.04,0:51:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你有很多同伴\N{\fe238}{\fs14}At least you'll have company.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.71,0:51:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这一定是东南厢房的地基\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This must be the lowest foundation of the southeast wing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.16,0:52:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾祖父在内战时透过地下管道\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your great-great-grandfather was involved in the Underground Railroad...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.53,0:52:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密将黑奴运送来北方\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...secretly transporting freed slaves to the North...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.67,0:52:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀疑就是偷藏在这些洞穴\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and I suspect these caverns came in handy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.05,0:52:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德，过来看看\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Alfred! Come up here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.45,0:52:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里就看得见，多谢了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I can see everything all right from down here, sir, thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.44,0:53:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,头罩的主要零件来自新加坡\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We order the main part of this cowl from Singapore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.24,0:53:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,透过傀儡公司进口\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Via a dummy corporation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.91,0:53:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Indeed. And then, quite separately...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.94,0:53:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这零件则是向中国公司订购\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...we place an order to a Chinese company for these.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.41,0:53:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-然后我们自己组装 -没错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Put it together ourselves. -Precisely.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.55,0:53:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大量订购才不会让人起疑\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They'll have to be large orders, to avoid suspicion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.75,0:53:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-有多少？ -一万个\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-How large? -Say 10,000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.82,0:53:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-至少会有很多备用品 -是啊\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Well, at least we'll have spares. -Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.84,0:53:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不分一杯羹吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Don't suppose you want a taste.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.08,0:53:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想也许有一天你会学聪明\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I just keep offering, thinking maybe someday you'll get wise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.41,0:53:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么做一点都不聪明\N{\fe238}{\fs14}There's nothing wise in what you do, Flass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.75,0:53:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老詹，你不收贿让大家很紧张\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, Jimbo, you don't take the taste, makes us guys nervous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.28,0:53:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会告密\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm no rat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.89,0:54:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都被收买，我能向谁告状？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In a town this bent, who's there to rat to anyway?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.28,0:54:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别转身\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Don't turn around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.98,0:54:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你是硕果仅存的好警察\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're a good cop. One of the few.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.75,0:54:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What do you want?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.06,0:54:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,法康尼每星期都进一批毒品\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Carmine Falcone brings in shipments of drugs every week.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.39,0:54:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么没人阻止他？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Nobody takes him down. Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.59,0:54:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他收买了警察和法官\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He's paid up with the right people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.03,0:54:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么做才能制止他？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What will it take to bring him down?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.53,0:54:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,向斐登法官施压\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Leverage on Judge Faden...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.63,0:54:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,找一个有胆识的检察官\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and a DA brave enough to prosecute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.44,0:55:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋·道斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rachel Dawes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.64,0:55:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.17,0:55:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,注意我的信号\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Watch for my sign.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.48,0:55:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有一个人？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're just one man?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.95,0:55:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们有两个人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now we're two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.48,0:55:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.73,0:55:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,站住！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Freeze!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.65,0:55:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么人？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What the hell was that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.49,0:55:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一个疯子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Just some nut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.12,0:56:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你又要去洞穴探险吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, what is it today? More spelunking?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.09,0:56:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不，今天我要定点跳伞\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No. Today it's BASE-jumping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.16,0:56:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,定点跳伞？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}BASE-jumping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.36,0:56:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-像是高空跳伞吗？ -差不多\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-That like parachuting? -Kind of.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.13,0:56:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你有轻质布料吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Do you have any lightweight fabrics?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.10,0:56:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我正好有你要的布料\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You know, I think I have just the thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.11,0:56:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫记忆布料，看到吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's called memory cloth. Notice anything?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.88,0:56:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,和一般布料一样轻柔\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Regularly flexible...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.18,0:56:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一旦通上电流\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but put a current through it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.78,0:56:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-分子重新组合后就会变硬 -你可以做成什么形状？？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...molecules realign, it becomes rigid. -What kind of shapes can you make?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.65,0:56:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有骨架，什么形状都行\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Can be tailored to fit any structure based on a rigid skeleton.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.92,0:56:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,军方又嫌太贵吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Too expensive for the Army?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.32,0:56:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没想到亿万富翁会有兴趣 去洞穴探险或定点跳伞\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I don't think they tried to market it to the billionaire, BASE-jumping crowd.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.23,0:56:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-福克斯先生 -是的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Look, Mr. Fox. -Yes, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.70,0:56:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得不妥…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}If you're uncomfortable...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.23,0:56:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你不跟我实话实说\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Mr. Wayne, if you don't want to tell me exactly what you're doing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.60,0:56:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我被问到就不必说谎\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...when I'm asked, I don't have to lie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.34,0:56:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过别以为我是傻子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But don't think of me as an idiot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.44,0:56:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Fair enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.34,0:57:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.18,0:57:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那辆弹力车？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The Tumbler?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.65,0:57:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会有兴趣的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Oh, you wouldn't be interested in that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.62,0:57:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是造桥用的越野车\N{\fe238}{\fs14}She was built as a bridging vehicle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.53,0:57:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,作战时可以拉着缆绳跳过河流\N{\fe238}{\fs14}During combat, two of these would jump over a river, towing cables.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.50,0:57:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只要让推进器全速前进\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Over here on the throttle, flip that open and throttle up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.30,0:57:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它就能越过任何障碍 不要乱来！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This will boost you into a rampless jump... Not now!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.71,0:57:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小子，别乱来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Not... Not now, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.64,0:57:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭再燃装置\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Afterburner disengaged.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.91,0:57:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直没办法造桥\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We never could get the damn bridge to work...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.11,0:57:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这辆车性能超强\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but this baby works just fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.39,0:57:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎样？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So, what do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.89,0:58:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有黑色车款吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Does it come in black?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.53,0:58:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你星期四到码头\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I need you at the docks Thursday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.13,0:58:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-有麻烦吗？ -最后一批货…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Problems? -I don't want any trouble...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.20,0:58:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-最后一批货不能出错 -好吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...with the last shipment. -Sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.90,0:58:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,听说有一位检察官在找你麻烦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Word on the street is you got a beef with somebody in the DA's office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.74,0:58:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-是吗？ -听说你肯付…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Is that right? -And that there's a fat prize...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.31,0:58:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一大笔钱把她除掉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...waiting for anybody willing to do anything about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.18,0:58:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么，佛莱斯警官？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So, what's your point, Mr. Flass?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.61,0:58:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过那女孩吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Have you seen the girl?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.38,0:58:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个美女助理检察官\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's a cute little assistant DA.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.22,0:58:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拿她开刀不太好吧？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Don't you think that's a little too much heat to bring down, maybe?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.05,0:58:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-你会激起众怒 -别太高估哥谭市的治安\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Even for this town. -Never underestimate Gotham City.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.52,0:58:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都有人下班被抢\N{\fe238}{\fs14}People get mugged coming home from work every day of the week.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.52,0:58:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候就是会莫名其妙走霉运\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Sometimes... Sometimes things just go bad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.03,0:58:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这批货的石墨含量太高\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's a problem with the graphite, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.03,0:58:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,下一批货一定没问题\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The next 10,000 will be up to specifications.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.90,0:58:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-至少厂商给我们打了折 -是啊\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-At least they gave us a discount. -Quite.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.64,0:58:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议你最好暂时不要撞到头\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In the meantime, sir, may I suggest you try to avoid landing on your head?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.27,0:59:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么选择蝙蝠？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Why bats, Master Wayne?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.54,0:59:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠让我感到恐惧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bats frighten me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.08,0:59:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要让敌人一样畏惧我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's time my enemies shared my dread.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.07,1:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是干嘛？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.81,1:00:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,继续干活吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Continue.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.97,1:00:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来没问题\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Looks fine out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.03,1:00:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,玩具熊直接交给毒贩吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The bears go straight to the dealers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.10,1:00:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对，玩具兔要运到奈何岛\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yeah, and the rabbits go to the man in the Narrows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.94,1:00:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-这两种毒品有什么不同？ -你最好不要知道\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What's the difference? -Ignorance is bliss, my friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.14,1:00:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你惹不起那些大魔头\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Don't burden yourself with the secrets of scary people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.15,1:00:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小史？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hey. Steiss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.44,1:01:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小史？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Steiss?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.85,1:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.21,1:01:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What the...?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.65,1:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我最好去看看\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I better check it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.06,1:01:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不妙，你最好闪人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}There's a problem out here. You better bail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.35,1:02:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Where are you?!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.15,1:02:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.27,1:02:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快开车，哦，要命！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Take a ride. Oh, shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.72,1:03:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么东西？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What the hell are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.89,1:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是蝙蝠侠\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm Batman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.39,1:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好帅的大衣\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Nice coat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.09,1:03:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.66,1:04:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hold it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.03,1:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,给我滚远一点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That's right, you better run.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.43,1:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,法康尼派他们来杀你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Falcone sent them to kill you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.40,1:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么？ -你把他惹毛了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Why? -You rattled his cage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.77,1:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是什么？ -你的筹码\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What's this? -Leverage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.51,1:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-用来做什么？ -把坏人绳之以法\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-For what? -To get things moving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.41,1:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.81,1:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,像你一样\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Someone like you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.21,1:04:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想要伸张正义的人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Someone who'll rattle the cages.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.35,1:04:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐，你没事吧？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Ma'am? Everything okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.15,1:05:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们是法康尼的手下？ -逮到他们也没用\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Falcone's men? -Does it matter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.82,1:05:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,法康尼一样有办法脱身\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We'll never tie him to it anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.32,1:05:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这次他脱不了身\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I wouldn't be too sure of that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.47,1:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What the hell is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.91,1:05:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,把他放下来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Cut him down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.09,1:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(蝙蝠侠逮到黑帮老大)
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.76,1:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可原谅\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Unacceptable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.16,1:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管他是帮派死对头、守护天使\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now, I don't care if it's rival gangs, Guardian Angels...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.16,1:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,或是什么救世主\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...or the goddamn Salvation Army...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.40,1:06:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,把他抓起来，别让他出风头\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...get them off the street and off the front page.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.90,1:06:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,听说他是一个人，或是一个怪物\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They say it was just one guy. Or a creature.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.63,1:06:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是奇装异服的怪胎\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It was some asshole in a costume.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.84,1:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-干嘛？ -他抓到…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Yeah? -This guy did deliver us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.70,1:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,势力最大的黑帮老大\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...one of the city's biggest crime lords.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.64,1:06:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能在我的辖区动私刑\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No one takes the law into their own hands in my city.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.31,1:06:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.81,1:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-他这次难逃法律制裁 -斐登法官会罩他\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No way to bury it now. FINCH: There's still Judge Faden.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.44,1:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-我能对付斐登法官 -大家都说是一只蝙蝠干的？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I've got Faden covered. -What about this bat they babble about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.81,1:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他们作证说是大蝙蝠干的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Even if these guys will swear to being thrashed by a giant bat...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.98,1:06:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,法康尼还是被逮个正着\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...we've got Falcone at the scene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.32,1:06:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠侠把他犯案的证据都给我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Drugs, prints, cargo manifests. This bat character gave us everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.95,1:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那就起诉他吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Okay. Let's do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.92,1:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-蝙蝠是夜行动物 -也许是吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Bats are nocturnal. ALFRED: Bats may be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.22,1:06:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你也不能睡到下午三点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But even for billionaire playboys, 3:00 is pushing it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.66,1:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是过双重生活的代价\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The price for leading a double life, I fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.90,1:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你制造的戏剧效果很唬人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your theatrics made an impression.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.67,1:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,戏剧效果和障眼法…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Theatricality and deception...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.87,1:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,能打击犯罪 这是好的开始\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...are powerful weapons, Alfred. This is a good start.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.27,1:07:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你以后会一直受伤\N{\fe238}{\fs14}If those are to be the first of many injuries to come...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.24,1:07:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就要找很好的藉口\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...it would be wise to find a suitable excuse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.37,1:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说打马球\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Polo, for instance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.91,1:07:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不会打马球\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm not learning polo, Alfred.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.81,1:07:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,无缘无故受伤，缺乏社交生活\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Strange injuries, a nonexistent social life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.65,1:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一定会怀疑\N{\fe238}{\fs14}These things beg the question...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.28,1:07:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯·韦恩大少爷都在搞什么鬼\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...as to what exactly does Bruce Wayne do with his time and his money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.68,1:07:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这种人都做什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What does someone like me do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.22,1:07:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,开名贵跑车，泡漂亮女星\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Drive sports cars, date movie stars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.12,1:07:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,买一些别人买不起的东西\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Buy things that are not for sale.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.86,1:07:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,韦恩少爷，当你假装找乐子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who knows, Master Wayne, you start pretending to have fun...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.03,1:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也许真的会找到快乐\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...you might even have a little by accident.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.73,1:07:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.36,1:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-出了状况 -什么事？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-We have a situation. -All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.10,1:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,海巡队昨晚发现我们的货轮\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The Coast Guard picked up one of our cargo ships last night...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.47,1:07:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,船身受损，船员失踪 大概全都丧命\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...heavily damaged, all crew missing, probably dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.31,1:07:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,货轮载了一具微波发射器\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The ship was carrying a prototype weapon. It's a microwave emitter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.84,1:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是用来进行沙漠战争的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's designed for desert warfare, but it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.48,1:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是看起来有人…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It looks like somebody...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.45,1:08:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,启动了它\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...turned it on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.12,1:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,它能发射微波蒸发敌人的供水\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It uses focused microwaves to vaporize the enemy's water supply.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.50,1:08:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,货轮严重受损\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The damage to the ship was catastrophic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.60,1:08:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那具武器也…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The weapon itself is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.90,1:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不见了？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Missing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.24,1:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.80,1:08:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,韦恩先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Mr. Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.47,1:08:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这辆车好酷\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Nice car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.08,1:08:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的另一辆车更酷\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You should see my other one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.48,1:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他逮到警方抓不到的大坏蛋\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He's done something the police never have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.58,1:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能动用私刑\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You can't take the law into your own hands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.05,1:09:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,至少他在打击犯罪\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, at least he's getting something done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.79,1:09:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯，你来评评理\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce, help me out here. -Huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.29,1:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一个扮成蝙蝠的人一定有毛病\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, a guy who dresses up like a bat clearly has issues.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.69,1:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他把法康尼关起来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But he's put Falcone behind bars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.10,1:09:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,警方并不领情，那代表什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now the cops want him. What does that tell you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.63,1:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那代表他们嫉妒他\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They're jealous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.03,1:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,水池是装饰用的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Sir, the pool is for decoration...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.83,1:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不能下去游泳\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and your friends do not have swimwear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.00,1:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她们是欧洲豪放女\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, they're European.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.84,1:09:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要请你们离开\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm going to have to ask you to leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.11,1:09:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我再多小费也没用\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It is not a question of money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.98,1:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你看着…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, you see...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.18,1:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我要买下这家饭店\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...I'm buying this hotel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.75,1:09:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,新规定，从今以后水池可以游泳\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and setting some new rules about the pool area.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.32,1:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该颁奖给蝙蝠侠\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I think the Batman deserves a medal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.89,1:09:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,把他送进疯人院才对\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And a straitjacket to pin it on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.49,1:10:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.83,1:10:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.76,1:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rachel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.73,1:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你回来了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'd heard you were back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.20,1:10:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.44,1:10:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只是泡泡水，见到你真好\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Just swimming here. Wow, it is good to see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.04,1:10:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你离开了好久\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You were gone a long time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.14,1:10:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊，你好吗？ -老样子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I know. How are things? -The same.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.98,1:10:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,工作越来越辛苦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Job's getting worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.81,1:10:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠自己是不能改变世界的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Can't change the world on your own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.71,1:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有别的选择\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What choice do I have...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.45,1:10:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你只会忙着和辣妹泡水\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...when you're too busy swimming?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.52,1:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋，这…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rachel, all of...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.89,1:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切\N{\fe238}{\fs14}All this...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.95,1:10:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不是真正的我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's... It's not me. It's...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.42,1:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我的内心…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Inside, I am...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.26,1:10:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有这么肤浅\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I am more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.86,1:10:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快来嘛，布鲁斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come on, Bruce. Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.60,1:10:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们再去多买几家饭店\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce, we have some more hotels for you to buy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.43,1:11:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.03,1:11:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你内心深处仍是那个正直的小孩\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...deep down you may still be that same great kid you used to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.97,1:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在你外表底下是谁并不重要\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But it's not who you are underneath...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.01,1:11:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的所作所为才重要\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...it's what you do that defines you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.32,1:11:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱恩医师，谢谢你来访\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Dr. Crane, thanks for coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.08,1:11:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气，他想割腕自杀？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Not at all. He cut his wrists?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.12,1:11:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他想装疯脱罪，不过万一出事…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Probably looking for the insanity plea. But if anything should happen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.96,1:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还是保险一点比较好\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Of course, better safe than sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.33,1:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了了，我快发疯了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yeah, Dr. Crane, I can't take it anymore. It's all too much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.06,1:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要出去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The walls are closing in. Blah, blah, blah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.06,1:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再吃几天牢饭我真的会发疯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}A couple of days of this food, it'll be true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.60,1:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要什么？ -我要知道…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What do you want? -I wanna know...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.43,1:11:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么让我闭嘴\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...how you're gonna convince me to keep my mouth shut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.07,1:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不知道\N{\fe238}{\fs14}About what? You don't know anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.60,1:12:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你怕警方仔细查那批毒品\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I know you don't want the cops to take a closer look at the drugs they seized.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.94,1:12:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也知道你替囚犯进行人体实验\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And I know about your experiments with the inmates of your nut house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.27,1:12:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会先查出合夥人的底细\N{\fe238}{\fs14}See, I don't go into business with a guy without finding out his dirty secrets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.51,1:12:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你找来的打手\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And those goons you used.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.58,1:12:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I own the muscle in this town.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.58,1:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直替你把货运进来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now, I've been bringing your stuff in for months...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.51,1:12:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你的老板一定想大干一票 要算我一份\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...so whatever he's planning, it's big, and I want in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.02,1:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他会怎么说\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, I already know what he'll say.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.55,1:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该杀了你灭口\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That we should kill you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.82,1:12:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他在我的地盘动不了我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Even he can't get me in here. Not in my town.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.06,1:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看我的面具吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Would you like to see my mask?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.16,1:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我用它来做实验\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I use it in my experiments.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.10,1:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你这大恶人不会觉得可怕\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now, I'm probably not very frightening to a guy like you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.97,1:12:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不过疯子就会被吓死\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But these crazies, they can't stand it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.71,1:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,原来疯人院是你这疯子开的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So when did the nut take over the nut house?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.61,1:13:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都跟你一样\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They scream and they cry...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.28,1:13:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大哭大叫\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...much as you're doing now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.25,1:13:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他这次并不是装疯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, he's not faking. Not that one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.62,1:13:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会和法官谈谈 把他送到我的精神病院\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'll talk to the judge and see if I can get him moved...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.35,1:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他待在这儿没有救\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...to the secure wing at Arkham. I can't treat him here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.77,1:13:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一场大风暴即将来临\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Storm's coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.87,1:13:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你逮到法康尼让黑道很紧张\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The scum is getting jumpy because you stood up to Falcone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.04,1:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的搭档和法康尼挂勾\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's a start. Your partner was at the docks with Falcone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.74,1:13:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他有时候也帮黑道办事\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, he moonlights as a low-level enforcer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.81,1:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,毒品分成两半，一半交给毒贩\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They were splitting the shipment in two. Only half went to the dealers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.78,1:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那另一半呢？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Why? What about the other half?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.18,1:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-佛莱斯知道 -他不会说\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Flass knows. -He won't talk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.22,1:14:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定会跟我说\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He'll talk to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.95,1:14:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,罗柏局长成立专案小组追捕你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Commissioner Loeb set up a massive task force to catch you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.46,1:14:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-他认为你是危险人物 -你认为呢？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-He thinks you're dangerous. -What do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.76,1:14:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你想尽力帮忙\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I think you're trying to help.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.20,1:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有时候我会看错人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But I've been wrong before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.30,1:14:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，别慢吞吞\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come on, I ain't got all night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.37,1:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托，我有小孩要养\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Flass, I have kids to feed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.64,1:14:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不爱吃三明治吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What, they don't like falafel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.22,1:14:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,另一批毒品在哪里？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Where were the other drugs going?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.22,1:15:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I never knew. I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.56,1:15:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-我对天发誓 -对我发誓\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I swear to God. -Swear to me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.40,1:15:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都不知道\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I don't... I don't know. I never knew. Never.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.76,1:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那批毒品先送去给另一个人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They went to some guy for a couple days before they went to the dealers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.27,1:15:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.27,1:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他在毒品里加了其它的料\N{\fe238}{\fs14}There was something... Something else in the drugs...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.00,1:15:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-不知名的料 -什么料？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...something hidden. -What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.77,1:15:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道那批货被送到奈何岛\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I never went to the drop-off point. It was in the Narrows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.27,1:15:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-警察只有成群结队武装起来才敢去 -我像是警察吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Cops only go there in force. -Do I look like a cop?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.71,1:15:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No...!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.12,1:15:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这箱货柜\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is the one I'm talking about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.45,1:15:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-有问题吗？ -它不该存在的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What's your problem with it? -It shouldn't exist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.89,1:15:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,从新加坡出发时只有246箱 现在却有247箱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This ship left Singapore with 246 containers, but arrived with 247.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.93,1:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面一定有违禁品\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm guessing there's something I'm not supposed to find in there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.23,1:16:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不敢查法康尼老大的货柜\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Listen, counselor, we don't wanna know what's in Mr. Falcone's crate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.03,1:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在情况不同了，快打开来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Things are working a little differently now. Open it up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.14,1:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,(韦恩企业)
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.97,1:16:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What the hell is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.80,1:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你，大家都在说你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's you, isn't it? Everybody's been talking about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.54,1:17:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快进来！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Get in here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.91,1:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别的小朋友一定不相信的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The other kids won't believe me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.12,1:17:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,湮灭所有证据\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Get rid of all traces.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.56,1:17:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-放火把这地方烧掉 -好吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Better torch the whole place. -All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.48,1:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你不舒服吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Having trouble?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.99,1:18:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下来，喝口水\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Take a seat. Have a drink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.06,1:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来火气很大\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You look like a man who takes himself too seriously.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.99,1:18:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你应该降降火气\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Do you want my opinion? You need to lighten up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.96,1:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德？ 帮帮我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Alfred, help me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.57,1:19:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我中了毒…替我验血\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Blood. Take. Take poison. Blood poison.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.11,1:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,中毒，中毒了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Poisonous. Poisonous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.41,1:19:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.38,1:19:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯，我们为什么跌倒？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}... why do we fall?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.55,1:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-我昏迷了多久？ -两天\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-How long was I out? -Two days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.29,1:20:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是你生日\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's your birthday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.46,1:20:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你生日幸福快乐\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Many happy returns.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.93,1:20:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我有过这种经验，这次更强烈\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I've felt these effects before, but this was so much more potent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.93,1:20:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种迷幻药 被做成喷剂当作武器\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It was some kind of hallucinogen, weaponized, in aerosol form.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.67,1:20:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定是在夜店被人下了药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You have been hanging out in the wrong clubs, Mr. Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.80,1:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是我把福克斯先生请来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I called Mr. Fox when your condition worsened after the first day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.04,1:20:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我替你验血，把接受体合成物 和蛋白质催化素分离出来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I analyzed your blood, isolating the receptor compounds and the protein-based catalyst.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.28,1:20:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能说白话？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Am I meant to understand any of that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.45,1:20:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可以，我费了好一番功夫\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Not at all. I just wanted you to know how hard it was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.18,1:20:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-终于制造出一种抗体 -你可以制造更多吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Bottom line, I synthesized an antidote. -Could you make more?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.05,1:20:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算再吸毒吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You planning on gassing yourself again, Mr. Wayne?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.95,1:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道，泡夜店狂欢\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, you know how it is. You're out at night, looking for kicks...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.19,1:20:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,总是有被下迷幻药的风险\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...someone's passing around the weaponized hallucinogens...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.12,1:20:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我把手上有的给你 注射抗体后就不怕被下药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'll bring what I have. The antidote should inoculate you for now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.73,1:20:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德，很高兴见到你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Alfred, always a pleasure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.29,1:20:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,卢修斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Lucius.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.43,1:21:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-你真的不进来吗？ -我得赶回去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You sure you don't want to come in? -I have to get back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.27,1:21:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-请你转交给他  -谢谢你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I wanted to leave this. -Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.17,1:21:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rachel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.90,1:21:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看来有人在蜡烛两头烧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Looks like someone's been burning the candle at both ends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.31,1:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你昨晚一定玩得很疯 -今天是我生日\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Must've been quite an occasion. -It is my birthday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.18,1:21:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，今晚我不能来 我只是来送礼物\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I know. I'm sorry I can't come tonight. I was just dropping off your present.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.91,1:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有别的事要忙吗？ -我的上司失踪了两天\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You've got better plans? -My boss has been missing for days...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.61,1:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这代表我要开始找他的尸体了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...which means I should probably start by looking at the bottom of the river.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.52,1:21:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-瑞秋 -对不起\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Rachel.  -Excuse me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.88,1:21:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋·道斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rachel Dawes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.82,1:21:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁下的命令？ 无论如何都要把克莱恩找来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who authorized that? Get Crane down there now. Don't take no for an answer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.46,1:21:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,请李曼医师明天一早交出报告\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Call Dr. Lehmann, tell him we need our own assessment to the judge by morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.79,1:21:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么了？ -法康尼出事了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What's wrong? -It's Falcone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.79,1:21:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱恩把法康尼送到精神病院\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Dr. Crane moved him to Arkham Asylum on suicide watch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.46,1:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,阿卡姆精神病院在奈何岛， 你现在要去？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're going to Arkham now? It's in the Narrows, Rachel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.73,1:21:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你去狂欢吧，布鲁斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You enjoy your party, Bruce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.73,1:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-我得去工作 -你千万要小心\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Some of us have work to do. -You be careful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.24,1:21:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Happy Birthday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.54,1:22:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,(谁找到就是谁的)
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.22,1:22:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,少爷，客人就快来了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But, Master Wayne, the guests will be arriving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.52,1:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我回来之前\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Keep them happy until I arrive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.29,1:22:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,说笑话给他们听\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Tell them that joke you know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.31,1:23:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,玩得开心吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Having fun?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.15,1:23:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔？ 你这大人物怎么会跑来这里？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bill? Now, what's a big shot like you doing in a place like this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.92,1:23:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要一些资料\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I need some information.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.35,1:23:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,韦恩企业47-B、1-ME型产品\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The Wayne Enterprise 47-B, 1-ME.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.46,1:23:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,1-ME型\N{\fe238}{\fs14}1-ME.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.19,1:23:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,能够蒸发敌人供水的微波发射器\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's a microwave emitter. It was designed to vaporize an enemy's water supply.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.03,1:23:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,听说被实验用来在空中散播化学物\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rumor was they tested dispersing water-based chemicals into the air...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.43,1:23:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是不合法吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but isn't that illegal?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.10,1:23:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要这项实验的所有资料\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I want all the information on the development of this project...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.50,1:23:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻把备份档案和文件送来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...all data, files, backup disks, on my desk right away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.91,1:23:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你弄丢了吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Did you lose one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.61,1:23:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把这部门和档案部合并\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm merging your department with Archives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.45,1:23:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要开除你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And I am firing you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.85,1:23:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你没收到通知吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Didn't you get the memo?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.09,1:24:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Scarecrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.02,1:24:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Scarecrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.26,1:24:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Scarecrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.56,1:24:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯小姐，你不必来这里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Miss Dawes, this is most irregular.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.96,1:24:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我把报告都交给法官了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I have nothing to add to the report I filed with the judge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.03,1:24:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的报告有疑点 -什么疑点？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I have questions about your report. -Such as?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.47,1:24:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一个没有精神病史的５２岁中年人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Isn't it convenient for a 52-year-old man who has no history of mental illness...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.94,1:24:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会在起诉前突然完全精神崩溃？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...to have a psychotic breakdown just when he's about to be indicted?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.71,1:24:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到他的病情有多严重\N{\fe238}{\fs14}As you can see for yourself, there is nothing convenient about his symptoms.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.61,1:24:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-稻草人 -稻草人是什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Scarecrow. -What's "scarecrow"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.48,1:24:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,产生幻觉的精神病患\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Patients suffering delusional episodes often focus their paranoia...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.28,1:24:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都会幻想被外在力量迫害\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...on an external tormentor...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.55,1:24:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,通常是某种可怕人物\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...usually one conforming to Jungian archetypes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.99,1:24:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他的幻觉是稻草人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In this case, a scarecrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.86,1:25:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-他服了药？ -我专攻精神病药物学\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-He's drugged? -Psychopharmacology is my primary field.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.16,1:25:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我强烈支持用药物控制精神疾病\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm a strong advocate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.46,1:25:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他在外面呼风唤雨\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Outside, he was a giant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.83,1:25:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里只能乖乖听话\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In here, only the mind can grant you power.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.43,1:25:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你很得意，对吧？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You enjoy the reversal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.33,1:25:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为精神胜于肉体\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I respect the mind's power over the body.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.53,1:25:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我专门治疗精神病患\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's why I do what I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.24,1:25:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但我专门把坏人关进牢里 不是住在疯人院\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I do what I do to keep thugs like Falcone behind bars, not in therapy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.34,1:25:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我要另外请医师为他进行诊断\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I want my own psychiatric consultant to have full access to Falcone...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.81,1:25:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,包括验血 查出你到底给他吃什么药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...including blood work. Find out what exactly you put him on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.28,1:25:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-请他明天一早再来 -他今晚就会来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-First thing tomorrow, then. -Tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.95,1:25:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经通知了李曼医师\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I've already paged Dr. Lehmann at County General.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.82,1:25:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,随你便\N{\fe238}{\fs14}As you wish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.15,1:25:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这里请\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This way, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.26,1:25:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给你看样东西\N{\fe238}{\fs14}There's something I think you should see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.76,1:25:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们的药厂\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is where we make the medicine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.20,1:26:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你也该吃一点药，让头脑清醒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Perhaps you should have some, clear your head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.36,1:26:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道你来这里？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who knows you're here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.99,1:26:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who knows?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.83,1:26:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He's here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.27,1:26:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谁？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.70,1:26:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠侠\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The Batman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.44,1:26:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们该怎么办？ -有坏人闯进来…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What do we do? -What anyone does...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.54,1:26:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...when a prowler comes around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.24,1:27:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-报警呀 -你要把警察找来？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Call the police. -You want the cops here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.34,1:27:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,警察拿我们没办法\N{\fe238}{\fs14}At this point, they can't stop us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.31,1:27:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是蝙蝠侠会坏事\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But the Batman has a talent for disruption.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.01,1:27:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把他逼出去，让警察毙了他\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Force him outside, the police will take him down. Go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.42,1:27:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-那她怎么办？ -她没救了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What about her? -She hasn't got long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.68,1:27:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我下的药很强 她撑不住的，快去吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I gave her a concentrated dose. The mind can only take so much. Now go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.92,1:27:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,听说他很神？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The things they say about him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.39,1:27:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的会飞吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Can he really fly?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.09,1:27:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说他能隐形\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I heard he can disappear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.33,1:27:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很快就会知道\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, we'll find out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.63,1:27:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Won't we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.60,1:28:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这下你要自食其果了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Taste of your own medicine, doctor?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.37,1:28:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里搞什么鬼？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What have you been doing here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.34,1:28:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你替谁工作？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who are you working for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.18,1:28:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,忍者…忍者大师\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Ra's... Ra's al Ghul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.71,1:28:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,忍者大师死了，你替谁工作？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Ra's al Ghul is dead. Who are you working for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.75,1:28:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱恩？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Crane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.28,1:28:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱恩医师不在\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Dr. Crane isn't here right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.79,1:28:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想预约挂号…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But if you'd like to make an appointment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.70,1:29:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠侠，放下武器投降\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Batman, put down your weapons and surrender.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.33,1:29:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你被包围了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're surrounded.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.27,1:29:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-你还在等什么？ -支援警力\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What are you waiting for? -Backup.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.81,1:29:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-支援警力？ -蝙蝠侠在里面\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Backup? -The Batman's in there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.37,1:29:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,霹雳小组正赶来，如果你想冲进去…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}SWAT's on the way. But if you wanna go in now...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.71,1:29:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会跟着你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...I'll be right behind you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.74,1:29:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,等霹雳小组来了再说\N{\fe238}{\fs14}SWAT's on the way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.38,1:29:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-喂 -喂\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Hey. -Hey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.14,1:30:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么了？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What's happened to her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.55,1:30:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她被克莱恩下了迷幻药 引发严重的恐慌症\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Crane poisoned her with a psychotropic hallucinogen, a panic-inducing toxin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.32,1:30:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-我把她送到医院 -没有用，我能救她\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Let me get her down to the medics. -They can't help her, but I can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.99,1:30:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,把她抱下去，在小巷等我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Get her downstairs. Meet me in the alley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.13,1:30:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,法康尼也被克莱恩下了药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Crane's been smuggling his toxin hidden in Falcone's drugs...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.20,1:30:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他也在哥谭市的自来水管下药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and they're dumping it into the water supply.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.87,1:30:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-他想干什么？ -我不知道\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What was he planning? -I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.73,1:30:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他替法康尼工作吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Was he working for Falcone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.53,1:30:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他提到另一个更可怕的人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He mentioned someone else, someone worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.24,1:31:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我得赶快为她注射抗体\N{\fe238}{\fs14}She needs the antidote before the damage is permanent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.97,1:31:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-她还有多久时间？ -不久\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-How long does she have? -Not long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.08,1:31:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么声音？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.24,1:31:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-支援来了 -搞什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Backup. -What the...?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.00,1:32:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Excuse me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.30,1:32:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-她怎么样？ -她昏过去了，快走吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}How is she? -She's fading. We gotta go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.37,1:32:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我去开车\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'll get my car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.01,1:32:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我开了我的车\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I brought mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.21,1:32:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你的车？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yours?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.18,1:33:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要弄一辆这么炫的车\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I've gotta get me one of those.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.25,1:33:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-他开车逃走 -车款和颜色？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-He is in a vehicle. -Make and color?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.59,1:33:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是辆黑色的…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's a black...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.26,1:33:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,装甲车\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...tank.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.19,1:33:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,保持冷静\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Stay calm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.23,1:33:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你中毒了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You've been poisoned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.73,1:33:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我追上去了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm on him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.47,1:33:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢呼吸\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Breathe slowly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.64,1:33:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,撑着点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hold on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.22,1:33:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在干嘛？ -抄近路\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What are you doing? -Shortcut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.09,1:34:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,挡住他的去路\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Air One to ground, block that ramp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.47,1:34:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他无处可逃\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He's got no way off that roof.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.47,1:34:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,马上熄火，乖乖下车\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Turn off your engine. Step away from the car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.90,1:34:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-相信我 -启动武器系统\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Trust me. -Weapons system activated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.59,1:34:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙到底是谁？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who is this guy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.19,1:34:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-他去哪里？ -他在屋顶\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Where's he going? -He's on the roof.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.30,1:34:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-他走哪一条街？ -不在街上\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What street is he taking? -He's not on a street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.70,1:35:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他在屋顶上开车\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He's flying on rooftops.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.59,1:35:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他的车到底长什么样子？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}At least tell me what it looks like.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.90,1:35:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,算了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Never mind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.23,1:35:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,追上了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Got him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.47,1:36:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就跟在他后面\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Coming right up on his butt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.76,1:36:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嫌犯朝往州际公路开去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We're tracking suspect vehicle heading west on I-17.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.46,1:36:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-呼叫地面… -他甩掉我们了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Air One to ground.  -I lost him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.33,1:36:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去他的踪影， 九号出口已封闭\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We've lost visual. Exit 9 is blocked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.40,1:36:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去前面查查看\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We'll loop back to check the frontage road.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.57,1:36:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,启动秘密行动模式\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Stealth mode activated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.30,1:36:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,保持清醒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Stay with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.74,1:36:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What...? There he is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.89,1:37:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,撑着点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Just hold on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.33,1:37:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rachel!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.77,1:37:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,(福克斯给您的，阿尔弗雷德笔)
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.28,1:37:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-自来水管被下了毒药吗？ -没错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-They get any of this into the mains? -Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.82,1:37:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,通知自来水厂，一定有办法… 全市的供水系统都被下药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Notify the water company. There's gotta be a way to isolate it. -No. They put it all in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.85,1:38:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定花了几个星期下药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They must've been at this for weeks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.89,1:38:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,已经溶入全市的供水系统了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gotham's entire water supply is laced.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.22,1:38:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么没中毒？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Why haven't we felt the effects?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.66,1:38:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这种毒药必须从肺部吸入\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Must be a compound that has to be absorbed through the lungs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.17,1:38:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉如何？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}How do you feel?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.64,1:38:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是那里？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Where are we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.60,1:38:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-你为什么把我带来？ -我把你救回来，否则你就失常了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Why did you bring me here? -If I hadn't, your mind would be lost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.57,1:38:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-你中了毒 -是…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You were poisoned. -It was...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.81,1:38:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-是克莱恩下的药 -好好休息，克莱恩被戈登逮捕了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-It was Dr. Crane. -Rest. Gordon has Crane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.58,1:38:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,戈登警官是你的朋友吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Is Sergeant Gordon your friend?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.55,1:38:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能有任何朋友\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I don't have the luxury of friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.08,1:38:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你打镇定剂 你醒来后就会在你家\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm gonna give you a sedative. You'll wake up back at home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.58,1:38:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你要把这些交给戈登 千万不要相信别人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}When you do, get these to Gordon, and Gordon alone. Trust no one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.72,1:38:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是什么？ -毒药的抗体\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What are they? -The antidote.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.62,1:38:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一瓶给戈登，另一瓶大量制造\N{\fe238}{\fs14}One for Gordon to inoculate himself, the other for mass production.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.36,1:38:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大量制造？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Mass production?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.83,1:38:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱恩只是爪牙，我们要准备应战\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Crane was just a pawn. We need to be ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.11,1:39:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当你说你想拯救哥谭市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}When you told me your grand plan for saving Gotham...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.75,1:39:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我没把你送进疯人院是因为…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...all that stopped me from calling the men in white coats...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.78,1:39:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你不是为了追求刺激\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...was when you said it wasn't about thrill-seeking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.42,1:39:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-我并不是 -那这算什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-It's not. -What would you call that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.65,1:39:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,(高速公路大追击)
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.35,1:39:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-很精采的新闻 -没死人真是个奇迹\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Damn good television. -It's a miracle no one was killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.12,1:39:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我没时间遵守交通规则\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I didn't have time to observe the rules of the road, Alfred.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.06,1:39:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你一手创造了一个怪物\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're getting lost inside this monster of yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.33,1:39:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我利用这个怪物帮助人们 就跟我父亲一样\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm using this monster to help other people, just like my father did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.93,1:39:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲那么做\N{\fe238}{\fs14}For Thomas Wayne, helping others...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.66,1:39:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是为了证明给任何人看， 包括他自己\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...wasn't about proving anything to anyone, including himself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.03,1:40:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了瑞秋，她中了毒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's Rachel, Alfred. She was dying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.84,1:40:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她就在楼下，请你送她回家\N{\fe238}{\fs14}She's downstairs, sedated. I need you to take her home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.87,1:40:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都很关心瑞秋 但你已失去控制\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, we both care for Rachel, but what you're doing has to be beyond that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.67,1:40:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为了徇私，就会变成恶徒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It can't be personal, or you're just a vigilante.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.78,1:40:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-福克斯还在吗？ -在\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Is Fox still here? -Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.84,1:40:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把这些客人赶走\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We need to send these people away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.61,1:40:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能毁了布鲁斯·韦恩的名誉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Those are Bruce Wayne's guests. You have a name to maintain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.72,1:40:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎我的名誉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I don't care about my name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.78,1:40:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是你，也是你父亲的名誉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's not just your name, sir. It's your father's name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.69,1:40:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他只留下他的名誉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And it's all that's left of him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.99,1:40:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别毁了他的名誉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Don't destroy it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.87,1:40:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-厄尔先生 -生日快乐\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Mr. Earle. -Happy birthday, Bruce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.20,1:40:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.90,1:40:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,公司的股价如何？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}How did the stock offering go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.21,1:40:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,涨停板\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Prices soared.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.61,1:40:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,股票都是谁在买？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who was buying?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.01,1:40:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,基金和证券公司\N{\fe238}{\fs14}All kinds of funds and brokerages.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.11,1:41:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会懂的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's a bit technical.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.98,1:41:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,重点是\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The key thing is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.84,1:41:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-公司的未来很稳定 -那就好\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-...our company's future is secure. -Great.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.46,1:41:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是喝多了几杯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}A little the worse for wear, I'm afraid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.46,1:41:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你的计划是什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What was the plan, Crane?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.40,1:41:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么把毒药释放在空气中？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}How were you gonna get your toxin into the air?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.03,1:41:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草人，稻草人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Scarecrow. Scarecrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.50,1:41:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,替谁工作？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who were you working for, Crane?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.40,1:41:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太迟了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Oh, it's too late.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.20,1:41:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你阻止不了他\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You can't stop it now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.38,1:41:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.28,1:41:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-生日快乐，布鲁斯 -谢谢各位\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Happy birthday, Bruce. -Thank you. Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.45,1:41:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的那样东西\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And thank you for that item.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.88,1:42:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're welcome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.28,1:42:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道你会用来救人 -我已经救了一个人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I know you'll put it to good use. -I already have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.35,1:42:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要大量制造要多久时间？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}How long would it take to manufacture on a large scale?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.72,1:42:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,几个星期，为什么问？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Weeks. Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.99,1:42:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有人想利用自来水散播毒素\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Somebody's planning to disperse the toxin using the water supply.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.16,1:42:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,自来水不能让人吸入毒素\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The water supply won't help you disperse an inhalant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.19,1:42:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.76,1:42:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,除非用微波发射器\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Unless you have a microwave emitter powerful enough...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.43,1:42:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把水分蒸发\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...to vaporize all the water in the mains.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.77,1:42:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是韦恩企业弄丢的那一台\N{\fe238}{\fs14}A microwave emitter like the one Wayne Enterprises just misplaced.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.47,1:42:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,弄丢了？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Misplaced?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.87,1:42:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我多问几句就被厄尔开除\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Earle just fired me for asking too many questions about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.37,1:42:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你回公司大量制造抗体\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Go back to Wayne Enterprises now and start making more of that antidote.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.04,1:42:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,警方会需要大量的抗体\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The police are gonna need as much as they can get their hands on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.28,1:42:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我公司的保全卡被没收了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}My security clearance has been revoked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.58,1:42:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定会有办法，对吧？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That wouldn't stop a man like you, would it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.98,1:42:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I suppose not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.75,1:42:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-布鲁斯，你一定要见一个人 -我现在没空\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Bruce, there's somebody you must meet. -Not now, Mrs. Delane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.59,1:42:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,听听我念得对不对…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now, am I pronouncing this right...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.62,1:43:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,忍者大师？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...Mr. Ra's al Ghul?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.69,1:43:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不是忍者大师\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're not Ra's al Ghul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.03,1:43:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到他死\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I watched him die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.50,1:43:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,也许忍者大师不会死？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But is Ra's al Ghul immortal?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.30,1:43:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他有特异功能？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Are his methods supernatural?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.31,1:43:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你才是真正的忍者大师吧？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Or cheap parlor tricks to conceal your true identity, Ra's?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.58,1:43:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己在晚上化身为正义使者\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Surely a man who spends his nights scrambling over the rooftops of Gotham...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.25,1:43:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不会怪我有双重身分吧？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...wouldn't begrudge me dual identities.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.12,1:43:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我救了你一命\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I saved your life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.08,1:43:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我教过你不能对敌人手下留情\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I warned you about compassion, Bruce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.72,1:43:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你要对付的是我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your quarrel is with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.82,1:43:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,放过这些人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You let these people go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.56,1:43:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管去跟他们解释吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You are welcome to explain the situation to them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.13,1:43:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,各位\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Everyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.53,1:44:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,各位来宾请听我说\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Everybody?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.00,1:44:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.34,1:44:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要谢谢你们喝光我的酒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I want to thank you all for coming here tonight and drinking all of my booze.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.67,1:44:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说真的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No, really.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.41,1:44:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这种亿万大富翁\N{\fe238}{\fs14}There's a thing about being a Wayne...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.34,1:44:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,免不了会有很多人来白吃白喝\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...that you're never short of a few freeloaders, like yourselves...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.08,1:44:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我敬大家，谢谢各位\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...to fill up your mansion with. So here's to you people. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.95,1:44:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-够了，布鲁斯 -我还没说完\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-That's enough, Bruce. -I'm not finished.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.88,1:44:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}To all of you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.75,1:44:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些伪君子 你们这些酒肉朋友\N{\fe238}{\fs14}All of you phonies, all of you two-faced friends...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.32,1:44:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,装一副笑脸，一心想讨好我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...you sycophantic suck-ups who smile through your teeth at me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.56,1:44:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请你们别再来烦我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...please, leave me in peace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.33,1:44:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请你们走吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Please go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.30,1:44:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是开玩笑，快走吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Stop smiling, it's not a joke. Please leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.87,1:44:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,派对结束了，快滚\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The party's over, get out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.23,1:44:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你丢尽了你父母的脸，韦恩先生\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The apple has fallen very far from the tree, Mr. Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.91,1:45:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很有意思\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Amusing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.98,1:45:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有用 这些人都活不久了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But pointless. None of these people have long to live.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.58,1:45:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你对疗养院的注意 逼我不得不提早行动\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your antics at the asylum have forced my hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.25,1:45:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱恩果然是为你做事\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So Crane was working for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.59,1:45:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他利用蓝花提炼毒药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}His toxin is derived from the organic compound found in our blue flowers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.76,1:45:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,然后做成化学武器\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He was able to weaponize it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.99,1:45:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是影武者联盟成员？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}He's not a member of the League of Shadows?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.13,1:45:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是 他以为我们要勒索哥谭市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Of course not. He thought our plan was to hold the city to ransom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.40,1:45:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你其实要在哥谭市下毒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But really, you are gonna release Crane's poison on the entire city.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.10,1:45:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,然后看着市民因为恐惧自我毁灭\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Then watch Gotham tear itself apart through fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.01,1:45:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算害死数百万条人命\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're gonna destroy millions of lives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.11,1:46:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人活着也是痛苦\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Only a cynical man would call what these people have "lives," Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.61,1:46:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们饱受犯罪荼毒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Crime. Despair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.62,1:46:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,活着还有什么意思呢？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is not how man was supposed to live.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.35,1:46:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,数千年来我们影武者联盟都在…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The League of Shadows has been a check against human corruption...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.65,1:46:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,清除人间败类\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...for thousands of years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.32,1:46:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在古罗马制造瘟疫\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We sacked Rome. Loaded trade ships with plague rats.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.09,1:46:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,把伦敦夷为平地\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Burned London to the ground.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.66,1:46:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,每当人类文明腐败到极点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Every time a civilization reaches the pinnacle of its decadence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.66,1:46:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就会将它毁灭\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...we return to restore the balance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.79,1:46:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哥谭市还有得救\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gotham isn't beyond saving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.70,1:46:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我时间，这里还有好人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Give me more time. There are good people here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.56,1:46:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个城市无药可救了 我们渗透了每一个阶层\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You're defending a city so corrupt we have infiltrated every level of its infrastructure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.81,1:46:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,该出去玩了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Time to play.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.38,1:46:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我在牢里看到你时，你迷失了自我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}When I found you in that jail, you were lost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.21,1:46:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我相信你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But I believed in you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.48,1:47:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我消除你的恐惧，指引你方向\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I took away your fear, and I showed you a path.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.49,1:47:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我最好的徒弟\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You were my greatest student.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.02,1:47:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该站在我身边拯救世界\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It should be you standing by my side, saving the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.99,1:47:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我要站在你面前\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'll be standing where I belong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.26,1:47:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止你屠杀哥谭市市民\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Between you and the people of Gotham.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.06,1:47:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人救得了哥谭市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No one can save Gotham.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.00,1:47:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,当森林腐烂，野火会把它烧光\N{\fe238}{\fs14}When a forest grows too wild, a purging fire is inevitable and natural.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.87,1:47:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是这座伟大城市的末日\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Tomorrow the world will watch in horror as its greatest city destroys itself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.11,1:47:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这次没有人能阻止我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The movement back to harmony will be unstoppable this time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.64,1:47:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-你曾经试过毁灭哥谭市？ -当然了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-You attacked Gotham before? -Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.08,1:47:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们使用的方法越来越成熟\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Over the ages our weapons have grown more sophisticated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.88,1:47:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾经造成经济大萧条\N{\fe238}{\fs14}With Gotham we tried a new one. Economics.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.18,1:47:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们低估了像你父母这种…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But we underestimated certain of Gotham's citizens...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.32,1:47:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,善心人士的力量\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...such as your parents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.59,1:47:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,结果他们竟被帮助的对象打死\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gunned down by one of the very people they were trying to help.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.33,1:48:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,老百姓没饭吃被迫当强盗\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Create enough hunger and everyone becomes a criminal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.29,1:48:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你父母的死让哥谭市民心连心\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Their deaths galvanized the city into saving itself...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.93,1:48:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,勉强撑到现在\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and Gotham has limped on ever since.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.80,1:48:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要来完成任务\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We are back to finish the job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.30,1:48:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不会有理想主义者碍事\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And this time no misguided idealists will get in the way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.70,1:48:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟你爸一样狠不下心\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Like your father, you lack the courage to do all that is necessary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.57,1:48:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人敢阻止我们伸张正义\N{\fe238}{\fs14}If someone stands in the way of true justice...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.64,1:48:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就从背后捅他们一刀\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...you simply walk up behind them and stab them in the heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.71,1:48:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要阻止你的恶行 -你学不会…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I am gonna stop you. -You never did learn...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.05,1:48:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,耳听四面、眼观八方\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...to mind your surroundings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.28,1:48:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,正义就是有仇必报\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Justice is balance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.45,1:48:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你烧了我房子，差点害死我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You burned my house and left me for dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.29,1:48:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我们算扯平了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Consider us even.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.83,1:49:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,确定没有人活着出来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No one comes out. Make sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.44,1:49:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都逃出去了？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}They're all gone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.08,1:49:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-有多少重度病患逃出去？ -全部都逃出去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-How many from maximum security? -Every one of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.01,1:49:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,连环杀手、强暴犯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Serial killers, rapists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.01,1:49:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,把桥梁升起，别让他们进城\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Raise the bridges. We don't want any getting off the island.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.02,1:49:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，就这么办\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'll raise the bridges...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.62,1:49:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等支援警力来把那些神经病抓走\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...when I get every available unit out here to catch the homicidal maniacs...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.05,1:49:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-到时候再说吧 -快去吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...that are running loose out there. -Come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.10,1:49:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不是消防队员\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I hope you're not a member of the fire brigade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.88,1:50:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,韦恩少爷！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Master Wayne! Master Wayne!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.51,1:50:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你成天健身连木头都抬不动？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What is the point of all those pushups if you can't even lift a bloody log?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.51,1:50:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底做了什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What have I done, Alfred?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.61,1:50:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,韦恩宅邸…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Everything my family...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.71,1:51:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲的心血…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...my father, built...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.02,1:51:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,韦恩家族的精神不只是砖块瓦砾\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The Wayne legacy is more than bricks and mortar, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.12,1:51:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要拯救哥谭市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I wanted to save Gotham.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.19,1:51:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我失败了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I failed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.29,1:51:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么跌倒？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Why do we fall, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.76,1:51:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才能学会站起来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So that we can learn to pick ourselves up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.70,1:51:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是没放弃我，是吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You still haven't given up on me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.77,1:51:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,永远都不会\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Never.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.30,1:51:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Down!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.80,1:51:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,警察暴力，警察动粗\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Harassment! I see harassment!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.90,1:51:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看真正的警察暴力吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Maybe you'd like to see some excessive force?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.11,1:51:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拿了枪的疯子\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Madman with a gun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.27,1:51:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,市民对警方镇压行动…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}With residents furious...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.64,1:51:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,感到愤怒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}... at the unprecedented show of police strength to round up the inmates...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.31,1:51:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把桥梁升起来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We're about to raise these bridges.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.31,1:51:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是检察官，让我过去\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Officer, I am a Gotham City district attorney. Let me pass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.32,1:52:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-给我闭嘴！ -佛莱斯，别激动！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Just shut up! -Hey, Flass, cool it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.79,1:52:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hold these people back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.22,1:52:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,戈登，有人来找你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hey, Gordon. Somebody here to see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.39,1:52:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-你跑来干嘛？ -我们的朋友要我交给你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What are you doing here? -Our friend sent me with this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.93,1:52:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是解药\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It counteracts Crane's toxin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.63,1:52:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你用不着\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hopefully you won't need it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.26,1:52:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,除非有人把毒药释放在空气中\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Not unless he's got some way of getting that crap into the air.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.56,1:52:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，不准过桥了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}All right, last one across.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.70,1:52:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,三分钟内就要把桥梁升起来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}People, they want this bridge up in no more than three minutes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.84,1:52:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好赶快离开这里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Better get you off the island before they raise the bridges. Patrolman!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.84,1:52:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.66,1:52:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到我妈妈\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I can't find my mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.79,1:52:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.70,1:53:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What the hell are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.94,1:53:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,各位\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gentlemen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.94,1:53:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该行动了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...time to spread the word.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.21,1:53:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要引起一阵…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And the word is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.87,1:53:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大恐慌\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...panic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.46,1:53:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,(自来水厂)
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.69,1:53:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,水压突然上升\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Jesus. The pressure, it's spiking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.29,1:53:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Right there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.93,1:53:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那是奈何岛的地下水管\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That water main is right under the Narrows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.11,1:54:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.50,1:54:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是罗局长\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is Commissioner Loeb.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.23,1:54:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快向我报告\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come on, somebody talk to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.10,1:54:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,说话啊！\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.31,1:55:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,罗局长，我是戈登\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Loeb, Loeb. This is Gordon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.65,1:55:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生什么事？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What the hell is going on?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.18,1:55:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要支援，镇暴警察、霹雳小组\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We need reinforcements. TAC teams, SWAT, riot cops!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.79,1:55:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,戈登，镇暴警察都在你那里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gordon! All the city's riot police are on the island with you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.19,1:55:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都中了毒\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, they're completely incapacitated!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.52,1:55:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了，没人会伤害你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's okay, it's okay. No one's gonna hurt you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.36,1:55:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我就会伤害你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Of course they are!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.20,1:55:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-克莱恩？ -不，我是稻草人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Crane? -No. Scarecrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.93,1:55:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,戈登\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gordon...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.50,1:55:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没有警力了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...there's nobody left to send in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.30,1:55:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩下我一个人？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}So I'm on my own?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.11,1:55:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,奈何岛陷入一团混乱\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The Narrows is tearing itself to pieces.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.94,1:55:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们将毒药释放到全市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is just the beginning. If they hit the whole city...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.71,1:55:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就会引起哥谭市的大恐慌\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...there's nothing to stop Gotham tearing itself apart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.61,1:55:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们要怎么做？ -透过铁路系统\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-How are they gonna do that? -The train.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.68,1:55:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,自来水管沿着轨道到韦恩大楼底下\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The monorail follows the water mains to the central hub beneath Wayne Tower.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.68,1:55:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只要在韦恩大楼发射微波\N{\fe238}{\fs14}If the machine gets to the station...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.58,1:56:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就会把全市的供水蒸发\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...it'll cause a chain reaction that'll vaporize the city's water supply.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.22,1:56:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让哥谭市充满毒气\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Covering Gotham in this poison.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.99,1:56:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你帮我阻止他们\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'm gonna stop him from loading that train, but I may need your help.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.36,1:56:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要我怎么做？ -你会开手排档吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What do you need? -Can you drive stick?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.43,1:56:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在这里\N{\fe238}{\fs14}There you are!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.26,1:56:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,除了恐惧本身\N{\fe238}{\fs14}There is nothing to fear...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.43,1:56:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but fear itself!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.23,1:56:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你们…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I am here to help you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.76,1:56:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠侠会来救我们\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Batman will save us. He'll come.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.13,1:57:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-他一定会来 -不要看\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-He'll come. -Don't peek.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.67,1:57:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我是戈登，把桥放下来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}This is Gordon. Prepare to lower the bridge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.91,1:57:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说他一定会来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I told you he'd come.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.05,1:57:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.65,1:57:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你很可能没命\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You could die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.41,1:57:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,至少告诉我你是谁\N{\fe238}{\fs14}At least tell me your name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.12,1:57:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我在外表底下是谁并不重要\N{\fe238}{\fs14}It's not who I am underneath...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.29,1:57:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我的所作所为才重要\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but what I do that defines me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.96,1:57:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.95,1:58:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的听我的话，扮成一个怪物\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, well. You took my advice about theatricality a bit literally.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.48,1:58:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的恶行到此为止 -你跟警察才到此为止\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-It ends here. -For you and the police, maybe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.12,1:58:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我要对付的是整个哥谭市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}My fight, however, lies with the rest of Gotham.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.62,1:58:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我失陪，我要摧毁这座城市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now, if you'll excuse me, I have a city to destroy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.16,1:58:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-你以为我打不过他们？ -请便吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I can't beat two of your pawns? -As you wish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.67,1:58:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,全球定位系统连线\N{\fe238}{\fs14}GPS online.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.81,1:59:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,距离一百码\N{\fe238}{\fs14}In 100 yards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.90,1:59:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Gentlemen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.58,2:00:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谁下令把桥放下来？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who the hell authorized this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.36,2:00:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,距离韦恩大楼三英哩\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Distance to Wayne Tower, three miles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.70,2:00:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,水压把沿路的水管炸爆\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The pressure's moving along the mains, blowing the pipes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.50,2:00:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果波及自来水厂\N{\fe238}{\fs14}If that pressure reaches us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.03,2:00:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,全市的自来水管都会爆炸\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...the water supply right across the whole city is gonna blow!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.51,2:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在下一个街口右转\N{\fe238}{\fs14}At the next intersection, turn right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.09,2:01:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远都学不会\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You will never learn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.13,2:01:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.10,2:01:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没有新的招式吗？ -这一招怎么样？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Familiar. Don't you have anything new? -How about this?!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.85,2:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,您已抵达目的地，韦恩大楼\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You have arrived at Wayne Tower.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.43,2:02:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快疏散整座大楼\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Evacuate the building.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.90,2:02:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,楼下的自来水厂会爆炸\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We're on top of the main hub and it's gonna blow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.30,2:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,启动武器系统\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Weapons system activated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.57,2:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害的车\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Nice ride.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.85,2:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,准备攻击\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Armed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.36,2:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(水压过高)
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.79,2:02:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要怕，布鲁斯\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Don't be afraid, Bruce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:54.06,2:02:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，来吧\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Come on. Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.20,2:03:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是穿着披风的凡人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You are just an ordinary man in a cape.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:02.44,2:03:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不能伸张正义，不能阻止列车\N{\fe238}{\fs14}That's why you couldn't fight injustice, that's why you can't stop this train.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.47,2:03:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谁说我要阻止列车？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Who said anything about stopping it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.88,2:03:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太帅了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.58,2:03:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你学不会耳听四面、眼观八方\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You never learned to mind your surroundings!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.83,2:03:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于学会狠下心来了？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Have you finally learned to do what is necessary?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.63,2:03:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会杀你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I won't kill you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.37,2:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我也不必救你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but I don't have to save you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.65,2:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-会议已经开始了 -什么会议？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The meeting's already started. -What meeting?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.99,2:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,福克斯，我炒了你鱿鱼\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Fox, I seem to remember firing you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.43,2:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:15.16,2:05:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到新工作\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I got another job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.09,2:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你的工作\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.00,2:05:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谁有这个权力？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}On whose authority?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.33,2:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠侠上了头版新闻\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Batman may have made the front page...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.47,2:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯·韦恩只上了第八版\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...but Bruce Wayne got pushed to page eight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.90,2:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,(酒醉亿万富翁烧毁豪宅)
Dialogue: 0,2:05:34.24,2:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是布鲁斯·韦恩\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bruce Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.41,2:05:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你凭什么决定谁来掌管公司？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What makes you think you can decide who's running Wayne Enterprises?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.34,2:05:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-因为我是公司老板 -你在说什么？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-The fact that I'm the owner. EARLE: What are you talking about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.34,2:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,公司一星期前上市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The company went public a week ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.41,2:05:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我透过各种基金…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And I bought most of the shares.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.25,2:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,买下大半股权\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Through various charitable foundations and trusts and so forth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.88,2:05:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会懂的，重点是…\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Look, it's all a bit technical, but the important thing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.32,2:05:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的公司的未来很稳定\N{\fe238}{\fs14}... is that my company's future is secure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.99,2:05:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧，福克斯先生？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Right, Mr. Fox?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.56,2:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也没错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Right you are, Mr. Wayne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.59,2:06:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你没收到通知吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Didn't you get the memo?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.11,2:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-很抱歉我没告诉你 -不必道歉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-I'm sorry I didn't tell you, Rachel. -No. No, Bruce...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.51,2:06:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我才要道歉\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:28.74,2:06:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,齐利被枪杀那天\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The day that Chill died, I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.28,2:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你说了重话\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I said terrible things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.41,2:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是真话\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But true things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.81,2:06:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时是个懦夫\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I was a coward with a gun...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.82,2:06:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,正义不代表报仇，我要谢谢你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and justice is about more than revenge, so thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.65,2:06:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想着你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I never stopped thinking about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.79,2:06:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我们\N{\fe238}{\fs14}About us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.06,2:06:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你回来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And when I heard you were back, I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:53.86,2:06:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我就抱着希望\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I started to hope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:20.11,2:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是后来我发现你的面具\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But then I found out about your mask.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.01,2:07:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠侠只是我的化身\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Batman's just a symbol, Rachel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.45,2:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fe238}{\fs14}No. This...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.28,2:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的面具\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...is your mask.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:33.95,2:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的你是犯罪克星\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your real face is the one that criminals now fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.36,2:07:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我深爱的人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}The man I loved...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.06,2:07:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经离开我的人\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...the man who vanished...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.73,2:07:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他根本就没有回来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...he never came back at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.36,2:07:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他还在世界某个角落\N{\fe238}{\fs14}But maybe he's still out there somewhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.20,2:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天哥谭市不再需要蝙蝠侠\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Maybe someday, when Gotham no longer needs Batman...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:59.94,2:08:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我会再见到他\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...I'll see him again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:08:12.95,2:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-你证明我错了 -什么事？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Proved me wrong, you know. -About what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.68,2:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲会以你为荣\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Your father would be very proud of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.39,2:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我一样\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Just like me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:08:49.97,2:08:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你接下来有什么打算？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}What will you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:08:53.24,2:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,重新开始\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Rebuild it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.68,2:08:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一砖一瓦重建家园\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Just the way it was, brick for brick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:04.88,2:09:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟以前一样吗？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Just the way it was, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.25,2:09:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，怎么样？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Yeah, why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:09.65,2:09:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得可以\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I thought this might be a good opportunity for...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.65,2:09:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,加强地基的部分\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...improving the foundations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.29,2:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-东南角的地基吗？ -没错\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-In the southeast corner? -Precisely, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.93,2:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-挺好的 -我找不到黑帮老大绑在上面\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-Nice. -I couldn't find any mob bosses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.70,2:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-警官 -我现在是警长了\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Well, sergeant? -It's "lieutenant" now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.77,2:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你改变了现状\N{\fe238}{\fs14}You really started something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.47,2:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,坏警察不敢再乱来\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Bent cops running scared.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:44.61,2:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,人们也充满希望\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Hope on the streets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:46.28,2:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-但是呢？ -奈何岛仍然被罪犯控制\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-But? -The Narrows is lost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.41,2:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱恩和变态恶徒也没落网\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And we still haven't picked up Crane or half the inmates of Arkham that he freed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.92,2:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会抓到他们的\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.78,2:09:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以拯救哥谭市\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We can bring Gotham back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:58.62,2:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-道高一尺、魔高一丈？ -怎么说？\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-What about escalation? -Escalation?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.29,2:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,警察开始用半自动步枪 歹徒就买自动步枪\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We start carrying semiautomatics, they buy automatics.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.76,2:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们穿防弹衣，他们用达姆弹\N{\fe238}{\fs14}We start wearing Kevlar, they buy armor-piercing rounds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.29,2:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-然后呢？ -你戴着面具\N{\fe238}{\fs14}-And? -And you're wearing a mask...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:14.00,2:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,飞檐走壁\N{\fe238}{\fs14}...and jumping off rooftops.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.30,2:10:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就拿这家伙来说\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Now, take this guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.57,2:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人放火、无恶不作\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Armed robbery, double homicide.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:21.80,2:10:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟你一样爱玩变装秀\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Got a taste for the theatrical, like you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:25.30,2:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,犯案后都留下名片\N{\fe238}{\fs14}Leaves a calling card.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:29.91,2:10:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(小丑)
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.11,2:10:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我会查查他的底细\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I'll look into it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:38.41,2:10:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直没谢谢你\N{\fe238}{\fs14}I never said thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.98,2:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你也永远不用谢我\N{\fe238}{\fs14}And you'll never have to.{\r}
